Zanga-zangar Da Aka Yi A Amurka Ta Tashi
Masu zanga-zanga sun fito kan tituna na biranen Amurka da dama don jawo hankali ga rashin adalci na launin fata.
An shafe watanni biyu ana zanga-zanga a Portland, Oregon, tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu yayin da yake tsare a Minneapolis, Minnesota.
Gwamnatin Trump ta tura jami'an tarayya zuwa Portland, suna karawa zanga-zangar karin wuta.
Masu zanga-zangar yanzu suna zanga-zangar kasancewar tarayya a cikin birni.
A Seattle, 'yan sanda da ke amfani da walƙiya da kuma hayaki sun kama mutane 45 a ranar Asabar bayan zanga-zangar goyon baya ko kuma zanga-zangar Portland ta zama ta tashin hankali.
'Yan sanda sun ce fiye da jami'an' yan sanda 20 sun ji rauni.
A ranar Asabar da daddare, a Austin, Texas, an kashe wani mutum lokacin da wani ya harbe shi a wani gangamin Black Lives Matter.
Rahotanni na kafofin yada labarai sun ce mutumin na iya kusantar wata mota da bindiga kafin a harbe shi.
"Abin da na sani shi ne cewa wani ya mutu yayin zanga-zanga abin ban tsoro ne", in ji magajin gari Steve Adler na Austin a cikin wata sanarwa.
Adler ya ce yana "karyayyen zuciya kuma ya yi mamaki".
A Louisville, Kentucky, gungun masu zanga-zanga masu dauke da makamai sun yi kira ga adalci ga Breonna Taylor, wata mata 'yar fata da ta mutu a Louisville lokacin da 'yan sanda suka shiga gidanta ba tare da gargadi ba a kan "ba a ƙwanƙwasa" umarni kuma suka harbe ta.
Saurayin Taylor ne ya fara harba wa jami'an wuta, yana tunanin cewa su masu shiga ne.
An kori wani jami'in 'yan sanda saboda lamarin Taylor, amma ba a kai karar sauran jami'an ba.
Shugaban kungiyar NFAC, wani 'yan bindiga na baki da ke cikin zanga-zangar, ya ce yana son binciken 'yan sanda kan kisan Taylor ya zama mafi bayyane.
'Yan sanda sun ce mambobin NFAC uku sun ji rauni ranar Asabar lokacin da daya daga cikin makaman 'yan bindiga suka yi hatsari.
