Da yake magana da Welt am Sonntag, wannan na karshe ya kira ƙoƙarin Amurka na lalata "babban aikin gine-gine" a bayyane ya shiga cikin ikon mallakar Turai.
A farkon wannan makon, Majalisar Wakilan Amurka ta amince da gyara ga Dokar Amincewa da Tsaro ta Kasa, da nufin fadada takunkumin Amurka kan kamfanonin da ke da hannu wajen kafa bututun gas na Nord Stream 2 na Rasha.
A cewar daya daga cikin masu bayar da shawarar dokar, matakan na iya zama na kamfanonin da ke sauƙaƙa ko samar da jiragen ruwa, inshora, wuraren tashar jiragen ruwa, ko ayyukan haɗi don waɗancan jiragen ruwa, da kuma waɗanda ke ba da takardar shaidar Nord Stream 2.
Duka kamfanonin Turai da jami'an gwamnati sun sha yin tir da yunƙurin Amurka na tsoma baki a cikin manufofin makamashi na Turai ta hanyar sanya takunkumi kan Nord Stream 2, wasu ma suna kira ga Brussels da ta yi aiki kan matakan magance hakan.
