An kafa ranar zaben Uganda.
Hukumar zaben Uganda ta tabbatar da babban zaben ranar 14 ga watan Janairun 2021, wanda Shugaba Yoweri Museveni zai fafata da shahararren matashin mawaki Bobi Wine, zaben da a cikinsa jimillar 'yan takara 11 ke takara.
Wani mai magana da yawun hukumar zaben ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa an gayyaci 'yan takara zuwa hukumar zaben a wannan Alhamis don tattauna tsarin zaben.
Shugaba Yoweri Museveni, wanda ke da shekaru 76, ya kwace mulki a Uganda ta hanyar tashin hankali a shekarar 1986, ya gyara kundin tsarin mulki don ba shi damar jinkirta.
