Fiye da mutane 60 aka kashe a harin Sudan.
Rahotanni sun ce sama da mutane 60 ne suka mutu kuma akalla 60 sun jikkata a ranar Asabar yayin wani hari da aka yi da makami a wani kauye a yankin Darfur a Sudan, wanda ke fama da tashin hankali akai-akai, a cewar rahoton hukumar agaji ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da yammacin Lahadi 26 ga watan Yuli.
Harin da aka kai a kauyen Masteri a yammacin jihar Darfur "shi ne na baya bayan nan a jerin matsalolin tsaro da aka sanar a makon da ya gabata wanda ya haifar da kone kauyuka da gidaje da yawa, fashi da kasuwanni da shagunan, da lalata gine -gine ", a cewar sanarwar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya.
