A ranar Lahadi, Sudan ta ce za ta tura rundunar tsaro daga jihohi da dama a Darfur bayan sake fara tashin hankali a can, a cewar SUNA, kafofin watsa labarai na kasar.
'Yan IPOB Sun Kashe Jami'anmu Biyu A Enugu - DSS - Jaridun Hausa na Shugabanci.
Ma'aikatar Tsaron Jiha (DSS) ta ce a ranar Lahadi ne jami'an sintirin ta suka fuskanci hari kuma 'yan asalin kasar Biafra (IPOB) sun kashe jami'an ta biyu a Emene, jihar Enugu.
A cewar Dr Peter Afunanya, mai magana da yawun DSS ya rasa jami'ansa biyu a harin.
Ya ce wannan mummunan harin ta'addanci da aka kai kan hukumar an yi shi ne yayin da jami'an ke aiki, a fili harin da IPOB ya kai.
Ya ce hukumar tana mika ta'aziyya ga iyalan jami'an da suka mutu kuma tana addu'ar gafararsu.
Duk da haka, an dauki dukkan matakan da suka dace don tabbatar da cewa masu aikata wannan mummunar aikin da duk wanda ya shiga cikin wannan mummunar aikin an kama su nan take kuma a gurfanar da su a gaban alkali.
Bayan haka, za a gudanar da cikakken bincike kan lamarin.
Bugu da kari, hukumar ta kuma sake jaddada kudurinta na kara karfafawa da kuma aiki tare da sauran hukumomin tsaro domin kiyaye lafiyar jama'a da tsaro.
Don haka, hukumar ta bukaci 'yan ƙasa masu bin doka su gudanar da ayyukansu na yau da kullum ba tare da tsoro ba.
Masu zanga-zangar Seattle sun yi karo da 'yan sanda kan shirin 'karuwar' jami'an tarayya na Trump
'Yan sanda a Seattle sun yi amfani da harsasai masu walƙiya da kuma feshin barkono a ranar Asabar kan masu zanga-zanga da suka ƙona motocin gini a wajen gidan yarin, a cikin fushin jama'a game da shirin "taron" jami'an tarayya na Shugaba Donald Trump a manyan birane.
Sautin ƙananan fashewar da aka maimaita ya yi ta a titunan birnin a jihar Washington, kuma hayaki ya tashi daga wani yanki inda masu zanga-zanga suka ƙona tirela a wurin da ake gina gidan yarin.
Masu zanga-zanga sun sare tayoyin motoci kuma suka fasa tagogin tirela.
'Yan sanda da ke sanye da kayan aikin tarzomar sun fuskanci masu zanga-zangar, wasu daga cikinsu sun ɗaga umbrellas akan harsashin fure na pepper spray.
Jaridar Seattle Times ta nakalto 'yan sanda suna cewa an kama mutane 16 bisa zargin kai hari ga jami'an, hanawa da kuma rashin tarwatsawa.
Shugabannin Afirka da aka kore daga mukaman mulki.
A farkon wannan makon, sojojin Mali sun yi juyin mulki inda suka hambarar da shugaba Ibrahim Boubacar Keita.
Keita shine shugaban kasa na 15 da aka tilasta masa daga mulki a Afirka a cikin shekaru 10 da suka gabata.
A ranar 18 ga watan Fabrairun 2010, sojoji a Jamhuriyar Nijar sun hambarar da Shugaba Mamadou Tandja bayan ya gyara kundin tsarin mulkin kasar don ba shi damar wa'adi na uku.
A ranar 14 ga Janairu, 2011, juyin juya hali ya kifar da gwamnatin Firayim Minista Zine El Abidine Ben Ali, wanda ya gudu daga kasar bayan shekaru 23 a kan mulki.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairun 2011, zanga-zangar ta tilasta wa shugaban Masar Hosni Mubarak ya sauka bayan shekaru 30 a kan mulki, wanda ya ba da damar sojoji su karbe mulki.
A ranar 11 ga Afrilu, 2011, jami'an tsaro sun kama shugaban kasar Cote d'Ivoire Laurent Gbagbo bayan tashin hankali da ya biyo bayan zaben da aka ayyana Alasassne Ouattara a matsayin wanda ya lashe zaben.
A ranar 20 ga Oktoba, 2011, 'yan tawayen Libya da taimakon sojojin NATO suka kashe shugaban Libiya Moammar Gaddafi, wanda ya yi mulki na kusan shekaru 42.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, 2012, sojojin Mali sun yi tawaye kuma suka kama Shugaba Amadou Toumane Toure.
A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, 2012, sojojin sun kama Shugaban Guinea-Bissau Raimundo Pereira da tsohon Firayim Minista Carlos Gomes Junior dangane da zaben shugaban kasa da aka yi.
A ranar 24 ga Maris, 2013, kungiyar 'yan tawaye ta Seleka ta tilasta wa Shugaba Francois Bozize ya sauka, inda ya nada shugabansu Michel Djotodia ya yi mulki, amma shi ma ya yi murabus a ranar 10 ga Janairu, 2014.
A ranar 31 ga Oktoba, 2014, sojoji sun tilasta wa Shugaba Blaise Compaore, wanda ya shafe shekaru 27 a kan mulki, ya gudu daga kasar, amma kasa da shekara guda bayan haka sai magajinsa, shugaban rikon kwarya Michel Kafando, ya tilasta masa ya sauka, duk da haka daga baya aka maido shi.
A ranar 21 ga Janairu, 2017, Yahya Jammeh ya bar Gambia bayan ya rasa zaben shugaban kasa ga Adama Barrow.
A ranar 21 ga watan Nuwamba, 2017, Shugaban Zimbabwe Robert Mugabe, wanda ya yi mulkin kasar na tsawon shekaru 37, ya yi murabus daga mukaminsa bayan da majalisar dokoki ta fara muhawara kan tsige shi, kuma yayin da tsohon mataimakinsa, Emmerson Mnangagwa ya gaji shi.
A ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairun 2018, Shugaban Afirka ta Kudu Jacob Zuma ya sauka daga mulki bayan yunkurin tsige shi bisa zargin cin hanci da rashawa, wanda ya baiwa mataimakinsa kuma shugaban jam'iyyar ANC Cyril Ramaphosa damar zama shugaban kasa.
A ranar 2 ga Afrilu, 2019, Shugaban Aljeriya Abdelaziz Bouteflika, wanda ya yi mulki na shekaru 20, ya yi murabus daga mukaminsa bayan zanga-zangar kan tsadar rayuwa da kuma bukatarsa ta wa'adi na biyar.
A ranar 11 ga watan Afrilun wannan shekarar, sojoji sun kifar da gwamnatin shugaban Sudan Omar Hassan al-Bashir bayan zanga-zangar watanni hudu a kasar, matakin da ya share hanya ga kafa gwamnatin rikon kwarya da ta kunshi sojoji da fararen hula.
