Ya kuma ce direban bai bi ka'idojin saukar jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu ba ko ka'idojin jiragen sama masu saukar ungulu da kamfanin jirgin sama ya kafa.
Jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu, AW 139, samfurin Agusta Westland, ya yi saukowar gaggawa a filin wasan kwallon kafa.
