Wilfried Zaha na son barin Crystal Palace, in ji Roy Hodgson: "Ku kula da wannan sararin"
Kocin Crystal Palace Roy Hodgson ya yi wa magoya baya rauni kafin kammala kakar wasa ta hanyar bayyana cewa dan wasan gaba Wilf Zaha yana son barin kungiyar.
Dan wasan na kasar Ivory Coast ya shafe sama da shekaru biyar a Selhurst Park kuma yanzu ya bayyana cewa zai bar kungiyar, bayan da aka danganta shi da kungiyoyin kamar Arsenal da Bayern Munich.
A shekara 27 ya rage a gani ko wannan kungiya ta har yanzu tana sha'awar kashe masa kudi mai yawa, musamman a wannan bazara tare da rashin tabbas na tattalin arziki a wasan, bayan wani kamfen da Zaha ya zira kwallaye hudu kuma ya samu taimako biyar ga kungiyar Palace wacce ta kasa yin wahayi.
Da yake magana bayan wasan bayan ranar karshe, Hodgson ya gaya wa Alex Crook na TalkSport ya "duba wannan sararin" game da yiwuwar ficewar Zaha bayan ya yarda da cewa dan wasan gaba ya "bayyana" yana ganin makomarsa daga kulob din.
Har yanzu dai har yanzu yana da sauran shekaru uku a yarjejeniyar da ya yi da Palace kuma a bara sun ce za a bukaci fam miliyan 100 don a dauke shi daga kulob din.
Bangaren Hodgson ya rufe kamfen tare da rashin nasara bakwai a jere da kuma wasan karshe na karshe, ya sauka zuwa matsayi na 14 a cikin tsari.
Zaha da kansa ya ci kwallo sau daya kawai tsakanin tsakiyar watan Disamba da karshen kakar, wani bugun nesa a rashin nasara a Chelsea.
An ruwaito cewa ya mika bukatar canja wurin a bazarar da ta gabata a kokarin tilasta masa ya tafi, amma ba a samu nasarar yin kokarin sayar da Palace ba.
A wata alama ta kara karfin damarsa na barin, Zaha ya sauya wakilai a watan Janairu kuma fifikon sa a makonni masu zuwa zai kasance ya tabbatar da barin.
Zaha shine dan wasan da ya taka leda a cikin minti da yawa a Premier League a wannan kakar don Palace kuma dan wasan daya tilo na karkashin shekaru 28 da ya taka leda na mintuna 1,100 ko fiye, yana nuna matakin sake ginawa wanda zai iya zama dole a cikin tawagar tare da yiwuwar kudin da aka kawo don lambar 11.
Malaysia na neman 'yan kabilar Rohingya 24 da ake tsoron sun nitse a tsibirin
KUALA LUMPUR, Malaysia (AP) - Hukumomin Malaysia sun ce a ranar Lahadi suna neman 'yan gudun hijirar Rohingya da ake fargabar sun nitse bayan tsalle daga jirgin ruwan su a tsibirin Langkawi da ke arewacin kasar.
Zawawi Abdullah, wani babban jami'i a hukumar kula da harkokin ruwa ta Malaysia, ya ce bayanan farko na 'yan sanda sun nuna cewa daya ne kawai daga cikin mutane 25 na Rohingya da suka yi tsalle daga jirgin ya yi nasarar yin iyo zuwa gabar teku.
Zawawi ya ce, wanda ya tsira shi kadai ya nemi taimako daga 'yan sanda a daren Asabar kuma an tsare shi domin ci gaba da bincike.
Daruruwan dubban Musulmai 'yan Rohingya sun tsere daga Myanmar saboda matsin lamba na soja, kuma da yawa suna zaune a sansanonin 'yan gudun hijira da ke cike da cunkoso a Bangladesh.
Kasar Malaysia mai yawan musulmai ta kasance makoma ce ta yau da kullun ga jiragen ruwa da masu fataucin mutane suka shirya don yi wa 'yan gudun hijirar alkawarin rayuwa mafi kyau a ƙasashen waje.
Zawawi ya ce an tura jiragen ruwa biyu da jirgin sama a binciken.
Ya ce hukumar za ta kuma gargadi masunta na gida da hukumomi a makwabciyar Thailand don taimakawa a binciken.
Bai ba da ƙarin bayani game da jirgin ba.
A watan da ya gabata, hukumomin Malaysia sun tsare 'yan gudun hijirar Rohingya 269 kuma sun gano gawar a cikin wani jirgin ruwa da ake zargin mai safarar mutane ne a Langkawi wanda suka ce an lalata shi da gangan don haka ba za a iya mayar da shi cikin teku ba.
Daga baya hukumar kula da harkokin ruwa ta Malaysia ta ce an kwashe 269 daga wani babban jirgin ruwa wanda ake ganin mutane da dama sun mutu kuma an jefa gawarwakinsu cikin teku.
Firayim Minista Muhyiddin Yassin ya ce Malaysia ba za ta iya karbar sauran 'yan gudun hijirar Rohingya ba yayin da take fama da koma bayan tattalin arziki saboda annobar coronavirus.
Amma ya ce ba za a tura waɗanda suke ƙasar ba zuwa teku.
Malaysia tana da baƙi da ba bisa ka'ida ba fiye da miliyan biyu da kuma 'yan gudun hijira da masu neman mafaka 180,000 - ciki har da Rohingya 101,000 - waɗanda aka yi rajista da su a hukumar kula da 'yan gudun hijira ta Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya.
Amurka na kokarin kulla alaka tsakanin Isra'ila da Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa - Leadership Hausa Newspapers.
Gwamnatin Shugaba Trump za ta tura manyan jami'ai biyu zuwa Gabas ta Tsakiya a wannan makon, da nufin karfafa yarjejeniya ta tarihi tsakanin Isra'ila da Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa, don kafa huldar diflomasiyya.
Wasu jami'an diflomasiyya uku sun ce sakataren harkokin wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo tare da surukin shugaban kasar Donald Trump kuma babban mai ba shi shawara, Jared Kushner, suna shirin ziyarar lokuta daban-daban da kuma kasashe daban-daban a yankin a cikin 'yan kwanaki masu zuwa, domin karfafa gwiwa wajen sake kafa dangantaka tsakanin Daular da Isra'ila.
Ana sa ran Pompeo zai tashi a ranar Lahadi zuwa Isra'ila, Bahrain, Oman, Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa, Qatar da Sudan, a cewar jami'an diflomasiyya da suka nemi a sakaya sunansu saboda ba a kammala jadawalin tafiyar ko sanar da shi ba.
Kushner, a halin yanzu, zai tashi a karshen wannan makon zuwa Isra'ila, Bahrain, Oman, Saudi Arabia da Morocco.
Ana sa ran ziyararsu za ta kai ga sanar da cimma matsayi a cewar jami'an diflomasiyya, duk da cewa dukkansu suna da akalla manufa daya, don sasanta sharuɗɗan yarjejeniyar da Isra'ila a nan gaba.
An kuma shirya Pompeo ya gudanar da tattaunawa da kungiyar Taliban a Qatar kan batutuwan da suka shafi tattaunawar zaman lafiya, wanda zai zama muhimmin mataki wajen janye sauran dakarun Amurka daga Afghanistan.
Fadar White House da ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar ba su yi tsokaci ba kan ziyarar da ba za ta kasance wani bangare ba na kokarin gwamnatin Amurka na karfafa alakar dake tsakanin Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa da Isra'ila, duk da cewa ba ta cimma sulhu ba a gwagwarmayar da ke tsakanin Isra'ila da Falasdinu.
Buhari, El-Rufai Ya bukaci a yi murabus.
Wata kungiya da ke ci gaba da kokarin kare 'yancin dimokradiyya da hakkin dan adam a Najeriya mai suna Concerned Nigerians ta yi kira ga shugaban kasa Muhammadu Buhari da gwamnan jihar Kaduna Nasir El-Rufai da su yi murabus.
A wata sanarwa da ta fitar ga manema labarai a ranar Litinin, kungiyar ta jaddada muhimmancin kawo karshen kashe-kashe da ake yi a kudancin jihar Kaduna.
'Yan Najeriya masu damuwa sun la'anci abin da suka kira sakaci daga bangaren gwamnati.
A cewar kungiyar, kashe-kashen da ke gudana a Kaduna ba tare da amsa ta gaskiya daga gwamnati ba abin mamaki ne kuma abin bakin ciki.
Sanarwar ta ci gaba da cewa, "A ra'ayinmu, rayuwar dukkan 'yan Najeriya na da muhimmanci kuma ba ma goyon bayan kisan da aka yi a Kaduna a makonnin baya".
Game da wannan al'amari, Muryar Amurka ta tuntubi mai ba da shawara kan kafofin watsa labarai na Shugaban kasa, Bashir Ahmed, kuma ya ce, "gwamnati tana yin duk abin da ta iya don kawo karshen wadannan matsalolin".
Ba mu san su wanene waɗannan 'yan fashin ba, suna iya sa tufafi don su dace da mazauna yankin, don haka dole ne mu yi hankali don yin abin da ya fi dacewa.
Ahmed ya kara da cewa, "Bayan hare-haren, Tukur Buratai, Shugaban Ma'aikatan Sojojin Najeriya, ya tafi Kaduna don ganin wadanda abin ya shafa".
Sanarwar daga kungiyar Concerned Nigerians ta zo ne kwana daya bayan jaridu sun ruwaito wani harin a kudancin jihar Kaduna, wanda ya sha wahala daga wadannan hare-hare.
Gwamnatin Ghana da USAID Sun Samar Da Hanyar Ilimi Ga Yara Ta Hanyar Rediyo.
Gwamnatin Ghana, tare da hadin kai da Hukumar Ƙaddamar da Ƙasashen Duniya ta Amirka (USAID), ta ba da shirye-shiryen rediyo don yara ƙanana, waɗanda za su koyar da miliyoyin ɗalibai.
Ana gabatar da shirin na awa ɗaya kwana shida a mako, kuma ana koyar da su ta wajen wasa.
USAID ta samar da shirye-shiryen ilimi a Ghana, kafin yin kawance da gwamnati da sauran masu ruwa da tsaki don ƙaddamar da shirin rediyo.
Ministan Ilimi na Ghana ya ce an tsara shirin ne don yara ƙanana kafin su fara makarantar firamare, da waɗanda ke makarantar firamare, kuma za a ci gaba da shi ko bayan annobar coronavirus.
TETFUND Ta Sa Makarantun Masu Zaman Kansu A Asusun Bincike Na Naira Biliyan 7.5
Asusun amintar da tallafi ga ilimi na gaba, TETFUND, ya ce ya yi gyare-gyare don haɗa da cibiyoyin bincike na masu zaman kansu, da ba na jihar ba da kuma cibiyoyin ilimi a cikin dala biliyan 7.5 na Asusun Bincike na Kasa da aka ware don dalilan bincike.
Sakatare na Asusun, Farfesa Elias Bogoro, ya sanar da hakan a Abuja yayin kaddamar da kwamitin zartarwa kan hadin gwiwa tsakanin Ma'aikatar Kimiyya da Fasaha ta Tarayya da Asusun Tallafin Ilimi.
A cewarsa, tare da  National Research Fund (NRF) ya karu zuwa naira biliyan 7.5 a shekarar 2020 daga naira biliyan 5 da aka amince da su a shekarar 2019, TETFUND ta yi gyare-gyare don haɗa hukumomin da ba na gwamnati ba kuma sun gayyaci cibiyoyin bincike na masu zaman kansu ko cibiyoyin ilimi don dalilan bincike.
Shugaban TETFUND ya nuna kokarin da Ministan Kimiyya da Fasaha, Dr. Ogbonnaya Onu ya yi kan hadin kai kuma ya gode masa saboda dagewarsa da goyon bayansa ga ci gaban tattalin arzikin kasar.
Sakatare Janar na Ma'aikatar Kimiyya da Fasaha, Dr. Mohammed Bello Umar ya ce hadin gwiwar da ke tsakanin ma'aikatar da TETFUND na kan hanya don bunkasa tattalin arzikin Najeriya ta hanyar kimiyya da fasaha tare da samun cikakken kudade.
Za a gudanar da atisayen tsaftace muhalli a karshen wannan watan - Kabiru Getso - Freedom Radio Nigeria.
Gwamnatin jihar Kano ta bukaci al'ummar jihar da su yi amfani da ranakun Juma'a da Asabar a karshen watan domin tsabtace muhallinsu musamman a wannan lokacin damina, a kokarin magance matsalar ambaliyar ruwa.
Kwamishinan muhalli na jihar Kano, Dr Kabiru Ibrahim Getso, ya sanar da hakan a yau, a cikin wata sanarwa da mai magana da yawun ma'aikatar, Abbas Habib Abbas, ya sanya wa hannu jim kadan bayan kammala taron da masu ruwa da tsaki suka yi domin shirya ci gaba da aikin tsabtace muhalli da za a gudanar a karshen wannan watan.
Ya ce an dakatar da aikin tsabtace muhalli na dogon lokaci saboda annobar Corona wanda ya shafi rayuwar yau da kullun.
Dr Kabiru Ibrahim Getso ya kara da cewa a wancan lokacin, gwamnati ta yi amfani da damar da ta samu wajen fesa sinadarai masu hana kamuwa da cutar korona a makarantu, tashoshin jiragen ruwa, kasuwanni, masallatai da sauran wuraren ibada.
Ya ce Ma'aikatar Muhalli na shirin gudanar da zagaye na tsabtace muhalli a ranar Juma'a a wasu kasuwannin jihar da kuma ranar Asabar don tsabtace tituna da sauran yankuna.
Dr Getso ya yi kira ga al'ummar jihar Kano da su hada kai daga karfe 7 na safe zuwa 10 na safe a ranar Juma'a da Asabar domin tsabtace muhallin su.
Matsakaicin farashin gas na Amurka ya tashi da dinari guda a cikin makonni biyu zuwa $2.25/gallon
CAMARILLO, California. -- Matsakaicin farashin gas na Amurka ya tashi kasa da dinari a cikin makonni biyu da suka gabata zuwa $2.25 a gallon.
Wannan ya rage farashin famfo da kashi 56 a shekara guda da ta gabata.
Mai nazarin masana'antu Trilby Lundberg na Lundberg Survey ya ce ranar Lahadi shi ne karamin tashin farashin da aka gani tun karshen watan Afrilu.
Ta ce farashin danyen mai ya kasance a tsaye kuma akwai wadataccen isar da man fetur na Amurka don biyan bukatar.
A dukan ƙasar, farashin gas mafi girma a San Francisco Bay Area shi ne $3.27 ga galan.
Mafi ƙarancin matsakaicin shi ne a Baton Rouge, Louisiana, da dala 1.79 ga galan.
Matsakaicin farashin man fetur a binciken da aka yi ranar Juma'a ya kasance daidai da makonni biyu da suka gabata a $2.54 gallon.
An kori malamai 71 na makarantun firamare da sakandare daga makarantar don hukumar Tsaron Jiha.
Akalla malamai 71 na makarantun firamare da sakandare ne aka sallama ba zato ba tsammani a Makarantar Ma'aikatan Al'umma, mallakar jami'an SSS a Abuja.
An sallame su bayan sun yi kuka don a kyautata zaman lafiyarsu, amma sa'ad da suka fito don su nuna damuwarsu, an watsar da su ta hanyar harbi a sama don tsoratar da su.
Wasikar sallama da aka rarraba wa kowane malami a ranar 2 ga Nuwamba, ta sauka a kan teburin PREMIUM TIMES.
Da farko kafin a sallame su, an gaya wa iyayen ɗaliban cewa kowane yaro ya zauna a gida na makonni biyu, domin makarantar ta iya yin gyare-gyare.
Amma abin da ya biyo bayan wannan shi ne sanarwar korar dukan malamai, daga shugaban makarantar firamare zuwa sauran malamai.
A makarantar sakandare ma an sallami dukan ma'aikata, daga shugaban makarantar zuwa ma'aikacin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Babban darektan SSS ya umurce ni in sanar da cewa an sallame su daga aiki.
Wannan saboda matsalar tattalin arziki da annobar corona ta haifar.
An umurci duk wanda yake da wani abu da ya shafi makarantar nan da nan ya mayar wa hukumar makarantar.
Malamai sun daɗe suna fama da rashin kula da lafiyarsu.
Iyaye kuma sun koka cewa duk da halin da ake ciki, an kara kudin makaranta daga N70,000 zuwa N90,000.
Malaman makaranta sun ce an rage musu albashi kuma an keta wasu hakkoki.
Gwamnatin Najeriya ta ce "haɗin Madagascar" ba ya warkar da cutar coronavirus.
Gwamnatin Najeriya ta ce babu wata alama da ke nuna cewa cakuda da aka shigo da ita daga Madagascar za ta warkar da kamuwa da cutar coronavirus kamar yadda ake ikirarin.
Ministan kiwon lafiya na kasar, Osagie Ehanire ne ya sanar da hakan, inda ya ce cibiyar binciken likitancin kasar ta fitar da rahoton bincikenta, wanda ya bayyana cewa maganin Madagascar yana dauke da sinadarai da zasu iya rage yawan tari amma ba magani bane ga cutar Covid 19.
Shugaban Madagascar Andry Rajoelina ya kaddamar da cakuda a watan Afrilu, yana mai cewa yana warkar da cutar coronavirus.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi gargadin kada a sha maganin da Madagascar ke samarwa ba tare da kulawar likita ba.
Madagascar, tsibiri ce a Tekun Indiya, ta ba kasashen Afirka maganin, wanda ta ce yana warkar da coronavirus.
A farkon wannan watan, Madagascar ta sake sanya takunkumin zirga-zirga a yankin Analamanga saboda karuwar kamuwa da cutar coronavirus.
Ƙasar kuma ta buɗe ƙarin asibitoci don magance wannan cuta da ke ci gaba da yaɗuwa a wasu ɓangarorin duniya.
Bankin Duniya zai ba da rance ga Kano da sauran jihohi - Freedom Radio Nigeria.
Bankin Duniya zai bayar da dala miliyan dari biyar a matsayin rance ga jihar Kano da wasu jihohi shida a kasar domin inganta ilimin 'yan mata.
A cewar Bankin Duniya, za a yi amfani da rancen ba tare da riba ba don inganta ilimin sakandare ga mata a jihohi bakwai.
Wannan ya kasance a cikin wata sanarwa da Bankin Duniya ya fitar a Abuja a yau inda ya bayyana cewa kudaden na daga cikin kudaden da Bankin ke bayarwa a matsayin taimakon ci gaba ga kasashe masu tasowa.
Jihohin da za su amfana daga rancen da Bankin Duniya ya bayar domin inganta ilimin mata sun hada da: Kano, Kebbi, Kaduna, Katsina, Borno, Plateau da Ekiti.
Hakazalika, sanarwar ta kara da cewa, kudaden za su taimaka wajen horar da mata a fannonin sana'o'i don aikin kai da kuma wayar da kan mata game da kiwon lafiya da sauransu.
Ba za mu bude makarantu yanzu ba - Minista - Freedom Radio Nigeria.
Gwamnatin tarayya ta ce har yanzu ba ta sanya ranar bude makarantu a kasar ba.
Ministan Harkokin Ilimi, Mista Chukwuemeka Nwajuba, ya sanar da hakan yayin da yake jawabi ga Kwamitin Task Force na Gwamnatin Tarayya na Anti-Corona a jiya a Abuja.
Ya ce har yanzu ba a warware batun komawa makarantu a kasar ba amma har yanzu ana ci gaba da tattara bayanai.
A cewar ministan, gwamnatin tarayya tana tattaunawa da masu ruwa da tsaki, musamman cibiyoyin ilimi na kasar, don neman mafita.
Wasu makarantun sakandare masu zaman kansu sun bukaci a ba su damar ci gaba da karatunsu amma gwamnati na son tabbatar da adalci ga dukkan dalibai wanda ya sa ba zai yiwu a amince da bukatarsu ba.
Nwajuba, a jawabinsa ya bukaci daliban da su kara hakuri da kuma duba karatun da suka yi a baya domin inganta iliminsu.
Poland za ta fice daga yarjejeniyar Turai da ta shafi hana cin zarafin mata
Gwamnatin Poland mai fafutukar dama ta ce za ta janye daga wata yarjejeniya ta Turai da ke da nufin hana tashin hankali kan mata.
Yarjejeniyar Istanbul ita ce takardar farko da ta shafi hana cin zarafin mata a duniya amma Ministan Shari'a na Poland, Zbigniew Ziobro, ya bayyana rubutun a matsayin "mai cutarwa" saboda yana buƙatar makarantu su koya wa yara game da jinsi daga mahangar zamantakewa.
Ziobro ya ce a karshen mako cewa a ranar Litinin zai fara shirya tsarin hukuma don ficewa daga yarjejeniyar.
"Wannan ɓangaren ra'ayi yana da alaƙa da buƙatar canza ilimin a cikin makarantu da kuma bayan shirye-shiryen makaranta, dangane da ilmantarwa, halaye, imani na matasa 'yan Poland masu koyo don yin, a ra'ayinmu, kuskuren cewa jima'i na halitta ya zama tsohon yayi, kuma a zahiri komai ya sauka ga jinsi na zamantakewa da al'adu".
A ra'ayin Ziobro, ba a yarda da abubuwan da ke cikin yarjejeniyar game da ilimin yara da matasa da kuma alaƙar dangi a cikin yanayin LGBT.
"Mun kuma ƙi ɓangaren LGBT na inganta alaƙar dangi, ra'ayi da masu fafutuka daga hagu ko ƙungiyoyin luwadi ke yadawa waɗanda ke son fassara imaninsu zuwa doka mai ɗaurewa", in ji shi.
