Sachin Pilot vs Ashok Gehlot; BJP ta ce jihar na cikin rikicin siyasa; Majalisa ta nemi gwajin kasa
Ashok Gehlot ya ce idan ya zama dole, Majalisa za ta gudanar da zaman-in-gidan-a waje da gidan Firayim Minista.
Wata rana bayan jagorantar darna a Raj Bhawan a Jaipur, Babban Ministan Rajasthan Ashok Gehlot a ranar Asabar ya ce idan ya zama dole, MLAs na Congress za su gana da Shugaban kasa kuma su yi zaman-tsaki a wajen fadar Firayim Minista don magance rikicin jihar.
A wani taron jam'iyyar majalisa ta Congress (CLP), Mr Gehlot ya nuna cewa shirin shine a yi gwajin kasa don tabbatar da cewa yawancin 'yan majalisar dokokin Congress da abokan huldarsu suna tare da shi a gwagwarmayar mulki.
"Ya ce gwamnati tana da rinjaye kuma tana son zuwa zauren majalisa", in ji wata sanarwa da babban shugaban jam'iyyar Mahesh Joshi ya fitar bayan taron CLP.
