Senegal, wacce tattalin arzikinta ya dogara da yawon bude ido don samar da kusan kashi 4 cikin 100 na kudin shiga daga kayayyaki da aiyuka na kasar a kowace shekara, ta ce mutane 9,422 sun kamu da COVID-19 tun barkewar cutar kuma mutane 182 sun mutu.
Kusan mutane miliyan 1.7 ne suka je hutu a Senegal a shekarar 2019.
Kasar ta dage haramcin jiragen sama na kasa da kasa daga ranar 15 ga watan Yuli amma ta ce za ta hana wadanda suka hana 'yan kasar Senegal shiga kasashensu.
Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta kafa cibiyoyin gwajin COVID-19 guda 4 a babban birnin Dakar don gwada matafiya, wanda a lokacin barkewar cutar akwai guda ɗaya kawai.
