Wakilin Yusuf Nadabo Isam'il ya ruwaito cewa a zaman zaman da aka yi a yau, Alkalin Shari'a Nura Sagir ya dage shari'ar zuwa ranar 29 ga watan Oktoba na wannan shekara.
Lauyan Abba Kabir Yusuf, Bashir Yusuf Tudun Wuzirici, ya ce shawarar da gwamnan jihar Kano ya yanke na sayar da kadarorin gwamnati ta saba wa dokar kula da filayen jihar Kano.
Barrista Musa Abdullahi Lawal, lauyan kwamishinan shari'a na jihar, ya ce korafin ba shi da tushe kuma ba shi da tabbaci.
