Jami'in FDNY mai bambancin ra'ayi ya ce 'da gaske' OK don cire fararen wuta daga masu tsaro masu launi
Wani jami'in FDNY mai bambancin ra'ayi ya ce 'a bayyane' ya dace a hana fararen 'yan wuta yin ado da launi don haka masu ɗaukar tutar su zama baki, a cewar wani sabon rahoto.
Farin dan wasan wuta Laftanar Daniel McWilliams ya shigar da kara da ikirarin nuna bambancin launin fata bayan an cire shi daga rukunin da ke dauke da tuta a watan Nuwamba 2017 taron tunawa da girmamawa ga membobin da suka mutu na Vulcan Society, kungiyar 'yan uwan yan wasan wuta baƙar fata.
Kuma babban jami'in bambancin da kuma hada-hadar FDNY, lauya Cecilia Loving, ta kare hukuncin a wani shari'ar da aka yi a bangaren 'yancin dan Adam na jihar New York, The New York Post ta ruwaito.
McWilliams na ɗaya daga cikin 'yan bindigar FDNY uku da aka gani a wani hoto na musamman yayin da suke ɗaga tutar Amurka a Ground Zero a cikin kwanakin bayan hare-haren 9/11.
A cewar korafin McWilliams, Hukumar Kula da Ayyukan FDNY ta zaba shi ya zama daya daga cikin masu dauke da tutar a cikin masu gadi masu launi a wurin bikin tunawa.
Kasancewa mai dauke da tuta a taron 'girma ce da gata' ga McWilliams, a cewar karar da ya shigar, CNN ta ruwaito.
Bayan isowarsa a taron, duk da haka, Shugabar kungiyar Vulcan Regina Wilson ta hana McWilliams shiga cikin masu tsaron launi saboda ta ce ta nemi mai tsaron launi baki a taron.
Sai ta tambayi McWilliams - tsoho mai shekaru 29 na FDNY - ya 'taimaka a wani matsayi dabam.'
Daga cikin waɗannan ayyukan an ce ya nemi ya raka fararen hula da kuma tara jami'an da ke sanye da kayan soja a cikin tsari daga taron.
McWilliams ya yi ikirarin cewa ya tambayi Wilson ko tana cire shi daga jami'in tsaro saboda ba shi da baƙar fata.
Ta tabbatar da cewa haka lamarin yake, in ji shi.
Wilson, wani tsohon soja na FDNY mai shekaru 21 wanda kuma ya kasance cikin kokarin ceto na 9/11 ya maye gurbin McWilliams da daya daga cikin membobin kungiyar Vulcan.
McWilliams ya yi ikirarin cewa ya bar wurin tunawa 'don ya ceci kansa daga ƙarin kunya, ƙasƙanci da kunya,' yayin da abokai da abokan aiki suka ji tattaunawarsu, in ji New York Daily News.
A lokacin da take ba da shaida a gaban kotu, lauyan McWilliams, Keith Sullivan, ya tambayi Loving - wadda baƙar fata ce - 'To, bukatar da aka yi na a saka wani mai baƙar fata a matsayin mai tsaro ba ta nuna wariya ba ne?'
'A'a, ba haka ba ne,' in ji Loving, a cewar New York Post.
Sullivan ya kuma tambayi Loving idan yana da kyau a nemi mai tsaron launi baki, wanda aka nakalto ta ce, 'Tabbas.'
A matsayin bayani, Loving ya ce ba laifi ba ne a canja farar fata da baƙar fata domin 'ta da mutuntakarmu da kuma ƙabilancinmu domin a saka wa juna fahariya da haɗin kai da kuma goyon bayan juna.'
McWilliams ya fara shigar da korafin nuna bambancin launin fata tare da FDNY a watan Janairun 2018.
Daga nan sai ya shigar da kara a kan Wilson, FDNY, birnin New York da kuma wasu mutane da ba a bayyana sunansu ba a watan Mayu na 2019.
Bayan shigar da kara, Sullivan ya ce magoya bayan Wilson sun yi ramako da McWilliams kuma sun tsoratar da shi.
A wani lokaci, an ce ɗaya daga cikin magoya bayanta ya kama McWilliams ya ce: 'Na ji labarinka, sun gaya mini za ka yi haka, kuma yanzu ka san ni.'
A cikin taƙaitaccen bayani, Sullivan ya rubuta cewa ƙin McWilliams daga matsayin mai tsaron launi na 'yan majalisa 'abin tausayi' ne kuma alamar ma'auni biyu a sashen kashe gobara.
'Idan kai baƙar fata ne kuma kana nuna bambanci ga farar fata a wurin aiki, za a yi maka bulala a mafi kyau,' in ji Sullivan.
Wilson, a cewar karar, ta sami 'sa'a daya na shawara' game da yadda ta bi da McWilliams.
A wannan lokacin, wani farin da ya nuna bambanci ga wani da launin fata yana karɓan 'zaɓe da azaba mai tsanani,' in ji Sullivan.
'FDNY ta kirkiro wata manufa da tsari na yin tawaye, ta fito da uzuri da kuma karbar 'yan kungiyar Vulcan ... wadanda suka aikata ayyukan wariyar launin fata, kuma dole ne a daina,' in ji Sullivan.
Noma ta inganta tattalin arzikin Najeriya, duk da matsalolin tattalin arziki.
Bangaren noma a Najeriya ya ba da gudummawa ga ci gaban tattalin arziki da kashi 24.6 cikin dari a watan Afrilu, Mayu zuwa Yuni, fiye da watannin Janairu, Fabrairu da Maris, da Afrilu, Mayu da Yuni 2019.
Ofishin kididdiga na kasa ya ce haka a cikin wani rahoto da aka fitar a ranar Litinin.
Rahoton da hukumar ta fitar a ranar Litinin, ya nuna cewa karfin tattalin arzikin cikin gida na Najeriya ya ragu sosai a watan Afrilu, Mayu da Yuni na 2020.
Ƙarfin Gross Domestic Product (GDP) shine ma'aunin cinikayya a cikin kayayyakin da aka samar a cikin gida a cikin ƙasa da kuma kwararar kuɗi a cikin ƙasar.
Bangaren aikin gona ya ba da gudummawar kashi 24.65 cikin ɗari a watan Afrilu, Mayu da Yuni na 2020, fiye da waɗannan watanni uku a cikin 2019, lokacin da ya kasance kashi 22.78 cikin ɗari.
Kuma ya fi na watan Janairu, Fabrairu da Maris na 2020, wanda ya kai kashi 22.96 cikin ɗari.
Wannan ya nuna ƙaruwa na kashi 19.90 cikin ɗari a daidai wannan lokacin na bara.
Wato, idan muka yi la'akari da hauhawar farashi da kuma tsadar kayayyaki, za a ga cewa bangaren noma ya ba da gudummawa kashi 23.9 cikin 100 na GDP na Najeriya.
Wato, noma ya inganta tattalin arziƙin da kashi 1.58 cikin ɗari na jimillar tattalin arzikin ƙasa, daga 2019 zuwa 2020.
Rahoton ya ce bangaren noma da kansa ya karu da kashi 6.57 cikin dari idan aka kwatanta da ci gabansa a watan Janairu zuwa Maris a farkon shekarar 2020.
Bangaren noma a Najeriya ya kunshi bangarori hudu da suka hada da samar da abinci, kiwon dabbobi, ci gaban gandun daji da kamun kifi.
PREMIUM TIMES ta ruwaito cewa, yawan kayayyakin cikin gida na Najeriya (GDP) ya yi ta girgiza da raguwa, irin ci gaban da ake samu a lokacin da ake haƙa rijiyoyi, tsakanin watan Afrilu, Mayu da Yuni na 2020.
Ofishin kididdiga na kasa (NBS) ya lura a ranar Litinin cewa matakan tsattsauran ra'ayi na kulle-kulle sun sa tattalin arzikin Najeriya ya ci gaba da koma baya.
Rashin tattalin arzikin ya kawo karshen abin da aka gani a matsayin ci gaban shekaru uku tun bayan rikicin tattalin arzikin Najeriya a 2016.
