A cikin makonnin da suka gabata gwamnati ta sanar da cewa ba za a gudanar da jarrabawar WAEC ba saboda annobar, amma yanzu gwamnati ta canza matsayinta.
Sojoji sun lalata sansanin 'yan bindiga, sun kawar da 'yan bindiga a jihar Zamfara
Aikin hana zirga-zirgar jiragen sama da sashen jiragen sama na Operation HADARIN DAJI ya gudanar ya lalata sabon sansanin 'yan bindiga da ke karkashin jagorancin shugaban 'yan bindiga da ake kira "Dangote" a yankin Dajin Doumborou na jihar Zamfara.
Mai kula da ayyukan yada labarai na tsaron, Manjo Janar John Enenche ya ce an kai harin, wanda kuma ya yi sanadiyyar kashe wasu 'yan bindiga da ke dauke da makamai, bayan rahotannin hukumar leken asirin dan adam (HUMINT) da kuma jerin ayyukan sa ido na sama.
Manjo Janar Enenche ya ce hukumar ta HUMINT ta tabbatar da cewa 'yan kungiyar, tare da kayan aiki, babura da daruruwan dabbobin da aka sace, sun koma sabon yankin daga inda suke a baya ta hanyar wani dutsen da ke cikin gandun daji.
Enenche ya ce, saboda haka, sashen sojin sama ya tura wani hadadden rundunar sojin sama na Najeriya (NAF) da jiragen yaki da jirage masu saukar ungulu don kai hari a wurin.
A cewarsa "jirgin saman harin ya kai hari yankin da aka yi niyya inda ya yi daidai kuma ya kashe wasu daga cikin 'yan fashin.
An ga wasu da yawa, da suke ƙoƙarin tserewa daga wurin cikin rikici, an shafe su a hare-hare na gaba".
Yayin da yake yaba wa sashen jiragen sama na Operation HADARIN DAJI saboda kwarewarsu, Shugaban Sojojin Sama (CAS), Air Marshal Sadique Abubakar, ya bukaci su ci gaba da dagewa wajen kai hare-hare ta sama kan 'yan bindiga.
Shugaban Sojojin Sama ya ba su aikin ci gaba da samar da tallafin iska na kusa don ayyukan ƙasa da ke gudana don kawar da duk 'yan bindiga da kuma dawo da al'ada a yankunan Arewa maso Yamma da Arewacin Tsakiya na ƙasar.
