Isra'ilawa na ci gaba da zanga-zanga kan yadda Firayim Minista ya magance annobar
JERUSALEM (AP) - Dubban Isra'ilawa sun gudanar da zanga-zanga da dama a fadin kasar a ranar Asabar, inda babban zanga-zangar ya gudana a Urushalima a wajen fadar Benjamin Netanyahu.
An yi zanga-zangar ne a cikin makonnin da suka gabata, wanda masu sukar suka yi la'akari da gazawar gwamnati wajen magance matsalar coronavirus bayan da ta fara kiyaye barazanar cutar.
Zargin cin hanci da rashawa da aka yi wa Netanyahu ya kara tayar da zanga-zangar.
"Bibi, ki tafi gida", in ji wata alama da wani mai zanga-zanga ya riƙe.
Wani allon ya ce "Kowa ya ga cewa sarkin ya rasa tufafinsa".
Daruruwan masu zanga-zanga sun kuma taru a ranar Asabar a wajen gidan rairayin bakin teku na Netanyahu a garin Caesarea mai tsada.
A makon da ya gabata, 'yan sanda sun yi amfani da bindigogin ruwa wajen tarwatsa jama'a a Urushalima.
Bayan abin da aka kira hanzari da rashin daidaito na sake buɗe tattalin arziki a watan Mayu, kamuwa da cuta ya tashi da matsakaicin adadin sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace rana a 2,000.
Tattalin arzikin kasar ya yi rauni saboda takunkumin cutar kuma yawan rashin aikin yi ya tashi zuwa kusan 20%.
Masu zanga-zanga sun ce tallafin da gwamnati ta bayar na taimakon kudi bai isa ba.
Zanga-zangar ta zo ne a cikin inuwar shari'ar cin hanci da rashawa ta Netanyahu wacce ta ci gaba a wannan watan.
Za a fara sauraron karar a watan Janairu.
An tuhume shi da yaudara, cin amanar jama'a da karbar cin hanci a jerin batutuwa.
Maurice Petty, mai gina injin Hall of Fame, ya mutu yana da shekara 81
KANSAS CITY, Kan. (AP) - Maurice Petty, wani ɓangare na daular tseren motoci wanda ya haɗa da mahaifin Lee da ɗan'uwansa Richard da kuma farkon mai gina injin da aka shigar da shi cikin NASCAR Hall of Fame, ya mutu a ranar Asabar.
Yana da shekara 81.
Iyalin Petty ba su bayyana dalilin mutuwar ba.
Ba a sanar da wani shiri na jana'izar ba.
Yayin da aka yaba wa sauran 'yan iyalin saboda iyawarsu a bayan motar, Maurice Petty ya sami laƙabin "Shugaban" saboda iyawarsa ta juya maɓallin.
Ya taimaka wa iyalinsa lashe tseren 198 da kuma zakara bakwai a cikin jerin manyan wasanni na NASCAR, kuma ya kuma gina injuna wanda ya jagoranci Hall of Famer Buddy Baker, Jim Paschal da Pete Hamilton zuwa nasara.
"Shugaban na ɗaya daga cikin manyan masu sana'a a tarihin NASCAR", shugaban kuma babban jami'in Jim France.
"Ya ba da ikon da ya taimaka wa ƙananan kamfanoni su bayyana mamayewa a wasanni.
Duk da yake an san shi da aikinsa a ƙarƙashin murfin, Maurice ya taka rawa da yawa a bayan fage, yana yin abin da ya kamata don taimakawa wajen kawo motocinsa zuwa hanyar nasara. "
An haifi Maurice Petty ne a ranar 27 ga Maris, 1939, a Level Cross, North Carolina.
Zai bi mahaifinsa zuwa hanya yayin da yake girma, kuma ilimin injiniya ba da daɗewa ba ya taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin Lee Petty ya lashe tseren 54 da kuma zakara uku.
Ya fara farawa 26 a cikin NASCAR Cup Series daga 1960-64, yana gamawa a cikin manyan 5 sau bakwai tare da 16 manyan 10.
Amma da sauri ya yanke shawarar mayar da hankali kan abin da ke faruwa a ƙarƙashin motar maimakon abin da ke faruwa a bayan motar, kuma wannan ya tabbatar da kyakkyawan mataki ga babban dan uwansa, wanda zai dogara da injunansa a lokacin mulkinsa.
Richard, wanda zai dauki sunan "Sarkin", ya lashe gasar farko tare da Shugaban lokacin da ya jagoranci Plymouth zuwa taken 1964.
Sun sake cin nasara a 1967, sun sake lashe gasar a 1970 da '71, kuma sun kara da wasu uku kafin shekarun 1970 suka ƙare.
Takardun bakwai sun kasance daidai da Dale Earnhardt da Jimmie Johnson don mafi yawan tarihi.
"Maurice Petty na ɗaya daga cikin ainihin majagaba a NASCAR wanda ya taimaka wajen gina ɗaya daga cikin manyan ƙungiyoyin NASCAR a cikin Ƙananan Kasuwanci", in ji darektan Hall of Fame Winston Kelley a cikin wata sanarwa.
"Ko da yake tarihin ya nuna nasarar 212 ne, Petty yana da nasara sama da 250 a cikin darajarsa idan aka yi la'akari da duk injunan da ya gina wa abokan hamayyarsa.
"Za a tuna da Shugaba har abada a matsayin daya daga cikin mafi kyawun gina tashoshin wutar lantarki a NASCAR".
Lee Petty ya mutu a 2000 kuma matar Maurice Petty ta shekaru 52, Patricia, ta mutu a 2014.
Shi kuma kawun tsohon direban da mai watsa shirye-shirye Kyle Petty ne da kuma shugaban tawagar Truck Series Trent Owens.
"Duk da cewa mun rasa daya daga cikin masu aikin farko na NASCAR, da jarumai, za a tuna da al'adun Maurice Petty da kuma tunawa da shi, a kiyaye shi, a yi bikin da kuma daraja shi", in ji Kelley.
"Muna mika ta'aziyarmu ga iyalin Petty".
Francois Bozize, shugaban CAR da aka tsige, ya sanar da neman shugabancin kasar
Tsohon shugaban Jamhuriyar Afirka ta Tsakiya da aka tsige Francois Bozize ya sanar a ranar Asabar cewa zai tsaya takarar shugabancin kasar a watan Disamba duk da cewa yana karkashin takunkumin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma yana da takardar kama shi saboda zargin aikata laifuka a kan bil'adama.
Ya sanar da hakan ne a wani jawabi da ya yi ga dimbin magoya bayansa a taron jam'iyyarsa, Kwa na Kwa (Aiki, Babu Abin da Ya Fi Aiki), a babban birnin Bangui.
An hambarar da tsohon janar kuma shugaban sojojin mai shekaru 73 a cikin tawaye na 2013 da kawancen 'yan tawayen Musulmi da ke arewacin kasar, wanda ya jefa kasar da ke da rinjaye a cikin yakin basasa da kuma rikicin jin kai mai tsanani.
"Kasar na bukatar mutum mai kwarewa, zaman lafiya da imani", in ji Bozize a jawabin da ya soki shugaban kasar na yanzu, Faustin-Archange Touadera.
Bozize ya fara karbar mulki ne bayan juyin mulki na 2003 kuma ya yi aiki shekaru 10 a matsayin shugaban kasa kafin ya tsere daga kasar a shekarar 2013.
Sabuwar gwamnatin ta nemi a kama shi saboda zargin aikata laifuka a kan bil'adama da kuma yunkurin kashe-kashe, amma ba ta yi wani mataki na kama shi ba tun lokacin da ya dawo daga gudun hijira a karshen shekarar da ta gabata.
Ba a bayyana yadda takunkumin ko takunkumin kasashen waje zai shafi takararsa ba.
A watan Janairu, Bozize ya ce zai nemi Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta janye takunkumin da aka sanya a shekarar 2014 saboda zarginsa na goyon bayan kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda na Krista masu yaki da Balaka.
Touadera na mulki a yau tare da goyon bayan wani babban aikin kiyaye zaman lafiya na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya tare da sama da sojoji 13,000 da 'yan sanda.
An zabe shi a 2016, ana sa ran zai nemi wa'adi na biyu a zaben amma har yanzu bai tabbatar da cewa zai tsaya takara ba.
An shirya zagaye na farko na tseren a ranar 27 ga Disamba.
Gwamnati ta rattaba hannu kan yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya a watan Fabrairun 2019 tare da kungiyoyi 14 masu dauke da makamai, wadanda galibi ke ikirarin kare bukatun wasu al'ummomi ko addinai.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, tashin hankali ya ragu, amma har yanzu akwai wasu mummunan lamura, yawanci ana ta fama da su ne saboda albarkatun da ake samu kuma yawancin kasar mai arzikin lu'u-lu'u ta kasance a waje da ikon gwamnati.
Rikicin ya tilasta wa mutane sama da miliyan 1.5 su gudu daga gidajensu.
