Masu zanga-zanga masu adawa da wariyar launin fata sun yi karo da 'yan sanda a Seattle
Rikicin da aka yi a Seattle tsakanin 'yan sanda da masu zanga-zangar nuna wariyar launin fata ya haifar da kama mutane da dama a ranar Lahadi, yayin da fushin jama'a ya tashi kan shirin "taron" jami'an tarayya na Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a manyan biranen.
An fara zanga-zanga kan wariyar launin fata da zaluncin 'yan sanda bayan mutuwar Ba'amurke Ba'amurke George Floyd a Minneapolis a watan Mayu.
Masu zanga-zanga a Seattle sun sare tayoyin motoci da kuma fasa tagogin tirela a lokacin zanga-zangar ranar Asabar, lamarin da ya sa 'yan sanda suka ayyana tashe-tashen hankula da share tituna da feshin barkono da kuma harsasai masu walƙiya.
Masu zanga-zangar sun kuma kona motocin tirela a wurin da ake gina wani gidan yarin da ke tsare da matasa.
'Yan sanda sun ce an kama mutane 45 yayin da jami'ai 21 suka ji rauni.
An gudanar da wannan gangamin ne don tallafawa zanga-zangar da ke gudana a Portland, Oregon.
Portland ta zama cibiyar tattaunawa game da matsin lamba da jami'an tarayya suka yi bisa umarnin Trump - wanda ba a goyan bayan jami'an yankin ba, wadanda suka ce jami'an sun yi amfani da karfin wuce kima.
Masu zanga-zanga sun yi gangami a Austin, Texas, da kuma Louisville, Kentucky; New York; Omaha, Nebraska; Oakland da Los Angeles na California, da Richmond a Virginia.
A Austin, an kashe wani mutum a harbin da ya barke a daren Asabar a wani zanga-zanga a cikin tsakiyar birnin Texas, in ji 'yan sanda.
Zanga-zangar ta zo ne yayin da Trump ke fuskantar gwagwarmaya mai wuya don sake zabarsa a watan Nuwamba, kuma yana yakin neman zabe a kan dandalin "doka da oda".
Kamfen din Biden ya ki amincewa da hirar 'Fox News Sunday', mako guda bayan taron Chris Wallace da Trump
A lokacin hirarsa da Chris Wallace a makon da ya gabata, Shugaba Trump ya yi tambaya ko dan takarar shugaban kasa na 'yan Democrat, Joe Biden, zai iya magance yawan tambayoyin da Wallace ya gabatar wa Trump.
Wataƙila ba za mu taɓa sanin amsar wannan tambayar ba.
A ranar Lahadi Wallace ya sanar da masu kallo cewa yakin neman zaben Biden ya fadawa Fox News cewa "ba shi da damar" don ganawa.
"A hirarmu da Shugaba Trump a makon da ya gabata, ya yi tambaya ko abokin hamayyarsa na jam'iyyar Democrat, Joe Biden, zai iya magance irin wannan gamuwa", in ji Wallace.
"A wannan makon, mun nemi kamfen din Biden don ganawa kuma sun ce tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa ba shi da wuri".
Ya daɗa cewa, "Za mu ci gaba da tambayar kowane mako".
Kamfen din Trump ya yi ta doke Biden tsawon watanni saboda ya ki gudanar da gangami da taron manema labarai yayin da yake ci gaba da yin tambayoyi a yayin annobar coronavirus.
Yayin da Biden ya dawo kan gungumen kwanan nan, Trump da kawayenta sun ci gaba da yi wa tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa ba'a saboda "ɓoye" a gidansa a Delaware.
Duk da haka, kin amincewa da Biden na gudanar da tarurrukan jama'a, bai yi illa ba ga takararsa kamar yadda kuri'un da aka yi kwanan nan suka nuna Biden yana da kyau a gaban Trump a kasa da kuma a manyan jihohin da ake fama da su.
Matsakaicin 'yan siyasa na gaskiya ya nuna cewa shugaban ya ragu da maki 7 a Florida, maki 6.7 a Pennsylvania, maki 8.2 a Michigan da maki 6.4 a Wisconsin.
Trump ya lashe jihohi hudu a shekarar 2016, ya sauya su daga shuɗi zuwa ja yayin da ya lashe Fadar White House.
Sabbin kuri'un Fox News sun sanya Biden a gaba a Minnesota, Michigan da Pennsylvania, tare da jagoranci duk a waje da kuskuren kuskure.
Binciken ya kuma nuna cewa Biden yana da ɗan galaba a Ohio, North Carolina da Arizona, wasu jihohi uku masu mahimmanci a wannan zagaye.
Kuma, binciken ya nuna cewa jihohin da suka kasance masu aminci kamar Texas da Georgia duk sun kasance tsakanin Trump da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa.
Zaben shugaban kasa wanda wani mai mulki ke neman wa'adi na biyu a fadar White House sau da yawa ana yin kuri'ar raba gardama ne akan wannan shugaban - kuma ana ganin hakan a halin yanzu a cikin takarar 2020 tsakanin Trump da Biden.
Manyan batutuwan sun kasance cutar coronavirus da tattalin arziki da cutar ta lalata - da kuma aikin shugaban kasa da rikodin a kan batutuwan biyu.
