Yanzu ita ce mai kula da ayyukan mata a wani ƙauye, kuma ta tuna cewa ba ta sami ilimi sosai ba domin talauci.
A lokacin da ta shiga cibiyar da farko, ta yi mamakin ganin irin kayan aiki na zamani da take da su.
Ta ce wannan cibiyar ita ce makarantar da ta fi dacewa da ita.
Daliban cibiyar suna samun darussa 6 a kowace rana daga Litinin zuwa Juma'a, inda suke koyon daidaitaccen Sinanci, doka, shari'a, ƙwarewar sana'a da kawar da ra'ayoyin masu tsattsauran ra'ayi.
A ranakun hutu na Asabar da Lahadi, suna zuwa taron addini.
Ta ce wasu kafofin watsa labarai sun ruwaito cewa cibiyar ta cire koda daga ɗalibanta kuma ta tilasta musu su yanke gashin kansu, wanda ta bayyana a matsayin mara tushe.
Ta ce tana maraba da wadannan kafofin yada labarai su ziyarci Xinjiang domin su ga halin da ake ciki, da kuma tattaunawa da daliban da suka taba samun horo a cibiyar.
Gwamnatin jihar Kwara da Dangote Foundation za su tallafa wa mata 15,000 a jihar.
Gwamnatin jihar Kwara tare da hadin gwiwar Dangote Foundation za ta raba Naira miliyan 150 a matsayin kudin tallafi tsakanin mata 15,000 don fara kasuwanci a yankunan karkara na jihar.
Mataimakin Gwamna AbdulRahman AbdulRazaq, Kayode Oyin-Zubair, ya yi sanarwar kan ci gaban al'umma a Ilorin a ranar Talata.
Oyin-Zubair ya ce za a bai wa kowace mace N10,000 a karshen shekarar 2020.
Ya ce gwamnati tana yin wannan ne don inganta yanayin rayuwar mutanen karkara don rage cunkoson a birane, don waɗanda ke cikin ƙauyuka su ma su iya yin kasuwanci maimakon zuwa birane.
Gwamnati za ta yi aiki tare da hukumar "Forestry Research Institute of Nigeria (FRIN) " don samar wa mata da tsaba na albasa don su ma su ci gaba da gasa a aikin noma.
Ya ce gwamnati za ta shirya tare da gwamnatin Kenya don kasuwanci da tsaba na lozenge a kasuwannin wannan kasa da kuma sauran kasashe.
A ranar 28 ga watan Oktoba, PREMIUM TIMES ta ruwaito cewa Gwamnatin Tarayya ta samar da tallafin N20,000 ga kowane daga cikin mata 2,800 na karkara a jihar Zamfara ta hanyar aikin tallafi ga mata na karkara.
Ministan jin dadin jama'a, agaji da ci gaban rayuwa, Hajiya Sadiya Umar Farouq, ita ma ta yi wannan sanarwar, inda ta ce wannan kasafin wani bangare ne na kokarin da Shugaba Muhammadu Buhari ke yi na cika alkawarin da gwamnatinsa ta yi na magance matsalar da al'umma ke ciki.
