Zulum ya rattaba hannu kan yarjejeniya da Jami'ar Al-Azhar don ci gaban Borno.
Gwamnatin jihar Borno a Najeriya ta rattaba hannu kan yarjejeniya da wasu jami'o'in Masar don bunkasa ayyukan kiwon lafiya a jihar da kuma horar da dalibai.
An yi wannan yarjejeniya ne a lokacin da gwamnan jihar, Farfesa Babagana Umaru Zulum, ya ziyarci Alkahira, Masar, inda ya ziyarci kungiyar tsoffin daliban jami'ar Al-Azhar a ranar Laraba.
Gwamna Zulum ya bayyana bukatar hadin kai wajen horar da malamai a makarantun sakandare na jihar Borno da kuma masu wa'azi.
Gwamnan ya kuma yi kira da a bude cibiyar Al-Azhar a Maiduguri, hedkwatar jihar, wato sashen koyar da harshen Larabci da kuma kafa reshen kungiyar Al-Azhar Alumni a jihar.
Zulum ya kuma ziyarci Jami'ar Ain Shams, kuma a Alkahira, inda ya gana da Shugaban Jami'ar. Sun tattauna batutuwa da dama da suka shafi hadin gwiwa da Jami'ar da jihar Borno a fannonin bincike na likita, a kokarin da take yi na kafa asibitin koyarwa na Jami'ar Jihar Borno.
Farfesa Babagana Zulum ya tattauna yiwuwar tura daliban likitanci zuwa Masar don karatun daban-daban wanda zai samar da dama ga ƙwarewa a fannoni daban-daban na kiwon lafiya.
Bayan taron na sirri, an kai wa gwamnan yawon shakatawa a sassan horar da likitoci da na kimiyya na jami'ar, inda ya sami cikakken bayani game da tsare-tsaren da aka gabatar. Farfesa Zulum ya gamsu da su kuma yana fatan ya karfafa shirinsa na inganta Jami'ar Jihar Borno.
Khartoum: Pompeo da Hamdok sun gana.
Firayim Ministan Sudan Abdallah Hamdok ya sanar da jerin ganawa kan muhimman batutuwa tare da sakataren harkokin wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo a Khartoum, ciki har da cire Sudan daga jerin kasashen da Washington ta ayyana a matsayin masu tallafawa 'yan ta'adda.
Pompeo ya isa Kartoum daga Isra'ila, wani yunkurin Amurka na karfafa dangantaka tsakanin Sudan da Isra'ila.
Ziyararsa na daga cikin ziyarar yankin, bayan cimma burin yarjejeniyar dawo da alakar da ke tsakanin Isra'ila da Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa a wannan watan.
Amurka na rokon sauran kasashen Larabawa da su bi sawun Abu Dhabi.
Tun da aka hambarar da Shugaba Omar Hassan al-Bashir, Washington ta sanya takunkumi a kan Sudan saboda zargin da ake yi na tallafawa kungiyoyin masu tsattsauran ra'ayi da yakin basasar Darfur.
Za a fara tsagaita wuta a gabashin Ukraine da ke fama da yaki da tsakar dare
KYIV, Ukraine -- Sojojin Ukraine da na 'yan tawaye a gabashin Ukraine da yaki ya addabe sun fara shirin tsagaita wuta "cikakke kuma mai zurfi" da aka shirya farawa da tsakar dare, matakin da jami'ai ke fatan zai iya haifar da karin matakai don magance rikicin shekaru 6.
Jami'an 'yan tawaye sun ce a ranar Lahadi sun umarci dakarun su game da tsagaita wuta kuma sun fitar da wata doka da ta hana amfani da makamai.
Sojojin Ukraine sun ce dakarunsu "sun fara shirye-shirye" don tsagaita wuta.
Idan aka tabbatar da shi, zai "shirya hanya don aiwatar da wasu sharuɗɗan" yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya ta Minsk, in ji ofishin shugaban Ukraine a farkon wannan makon, yana mai kiran tsagaita wuta "taɓawa".
A shekarar 2015 Faransa da Jamus suka yi matsaya, shirin zaman lafiya na Minsk ya yi niyyar warware rikicin tsakanin Ukraine da 'yan ware kai da Rasha ke goyon baya wanda ya barke a shekarar 2014 bayan da Rasha ta kwace Crimea da kuma goyon bayan 'yan ware kai.
Tun daga lokacin, yaƙin ya kashe mutane fiye da 14,000.
Shugabannin Rasha da Ukraine duk sun yaba da yarjejeniyar tsagaita wuta a cikin wata hira ta waya a ranar Lahadi kuma sun jaddada mahimmancin aiwatar da yarjejeniyar da aka cimma a taron kolin watan Disamba a Paris.
Shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin ya nuna damuwa game da kiraye-kirayen Kiev don sake duba yarjejeniyar Minsk kuma ya ce "tsayin da shugaban Ukraine Volodymyr Zelenskiy ya dauka game da yanayin da ba na madadin yarjejeniyar Minsk ba, wanda aka sake bayyana a yayin wannan kiran, ya kamata a fassara shi zuwa ainihin ayyuka", in ji Kremlin.
Zelenskiy a nasa bangaren, ya jaddada bukatar "ƙarin matakai na aiki" da nufin sakin 'yan Ukraine da 'yan tawaye suka tsare a gabashin Ukraine, a yankin da aka kwace na Crimea da kuma Rasha, a cewar wata sanarwa daga ofishinsa.
Yarjejeniyar ta 2015 ta yi la'akari da cewa Ukraine za ta iya sake samun iko a kan iyakarta da Rasha a yankunan da ke karkashin 'yan ware bayan an ba su ikon kai da kuma gudanar da zaben kananan hukumomi.
Yarjejeniyar ta taimaka wajen rage girman tashin hankali, amma dakarun Ukraine da 'yan tawaye sun ci gaba da musayar salvos na bindiga da harbi.
A watan Disamba, shugabannin Ukraine, Rasha, Faransa da Jamus sun hadu a Paris don sake zagayen tattaunawa, suna nuna goyon baya ga yarjejeniyar Minsk kuma sun amince da farfado da tsarin zaman lafiya.
Zelenskiy, wanda ya lashe zaben 2019 bisa alkawuran kawo karshen rikicin, yana son Ukraine ta fara sarrafa kan iyakokinta kafin zaben kananan hukumomi, amma Kremlin ya dage cewa ya kamata a aiwatar da yarjejeniyar ba tare da gyara ba.
Sabon yarjejeniyar tsagaita wuta an cimma ta ne a ranar Laraba ta bangaren mambobin kungiyar tuntuba ta uku da ta kunshi wakilan Rasha, Ukraine da kungiyar tsaro da hadin kai a Turai, kuma jami'an EU sun yi maraba da ita.
A lokacin da yake yi wa jama'a addu'a a ranar Lahadi a filin St. Peter, Paparoma Francis ya yaba da tsagaita wuta, ya kara da cewa ana bukatar a aiwatar da ita ′′don sake gina amana da kuma kafa tushe don sasantawa da ake bukata da kuma dadewa da ake jira tare da mutane. "
Ciwon zuciya: Cin cakulan sau ɗaya a mako zai rage haɗarin kamuwa da wannan mummunar cuta
Wani sabon bincike ya nuna cewa wasu abubuwa da ake sha suna da kyau ga jijiyoyin zuciya.
Kuma ta yaya zai rage yiwuwar ciwon zuciya?
Masu bincike sun gudanar da bincike na shekaru hamsin suna duba cutar zuciya ta zuciya (CHD).
CHD - wanda ake kira da ciwon zuciya na ischemic - yana da alamun farko uku: ciwon kirji (angina), bugun zuciya da kuma kasawar zuciya.
Wasu alamun cutar za su iya haɗa da bugun zuciya da kuma rashin numfashi.
"Cokelat yana ɗauke da abubuwa masu gina jiki da suke da amfani ga zuciya kamar su flavonoids, methylxanthines, polyphenols da stearic acid da za su iya rage kumburi kuma su ƙara yawan ƙwayar cholesterol mai kyau".
Kolesterol mai kyau, wanda ake kira high-density lipoprotein (HDL), yana tara "mummunan" cholesterol - irin wanda yake kwarara a jijiyoyin zuciya - kuma ya kai shi ga hanta.
A cikin hanta, ana rushe "mummunan" (lipoprotein mai ƙarancin ƙarfi) cholesterol kuma a fitar da shi daga jiki.
Duk da haka, sabon binciken bai bincika girman rabo ba, ko kuma irin cakulan da ake ci.
Ba a bayyana ko mahalarta sun ci cakulan mai duhu, cakulan madara ko wasu kayan zaki na koko.
An yi wannan binciken ne bisa bincike da aka yi a baya da ya nuna cewa shan koko (wanda ake samu a cakulan) yana rage haɗarin kamuwa da ciwon zuciya.
Masana kimiyya sun gaskata cewa flavonoids da ake samu a cakulan suna rage matsin jini kuma suna inganta aikin jijiyoyin jini.
Aikin jijiyoyin jini yana nufin yadda jini yake isar da iskar oxygen da kuma abubuwan gina jiki a cikin jiki da kuma kawar da sharar gida.
Game da sabon binciken, ba a nuna abubuwan salon rayuwa a cikin sakamakon ba.
Dokta Alice Lichtenstein ta yi sharhi a kan bayanan, ta ce waɗanda suka yarda cewa suna cin cakulan suna iya samun "nauyin jiki mai kyau".
Ta daɗa cewa za su iya "aiki na jiki a kai a kai" kuma su "rage matsin".
Ta ci gaba: "Kowane abu zai iya shafan lafiyar zuciya".
