Sama da mutane 13.85 lakh da suka kamu da cutar korona a Indiya ya zuwa yanzu, 32,063 sun mutu, 63.91% na masu warkewa
Jimillar mutane 8,85,577 sun warke kuma yawan warkewar ya kai kashi 63.91.
New Delhi: Indiya ta bayar da rahoton kamuwa da cutar korona 48,661 a cikin awanni 24 da suka gabata, inda ya kai jimillar ta zuwa yanzu 13,85,522, kamar yadda bayanan gwamnati suka nuna.
Adadin wadanda suka mutu ya tashi zuwa 32,063, tare da mutuwar 705 a cikin awanni 24 da suka gabata.
Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ya ninka cikin kusan makonni uku tun daga ranar 2 ga watan Yuli, lokacin da kasar ta wuce alamar lakara shida.
Yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar Covid a kasar ya kai alamar Lakh 10 a ranar Juma'ar da ta gabata.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami sabbin kamuwa da cutar kusan miliyan uku. Wannan shi ne rana ta huɗu a jere da masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 suka ƙaru da fiye da 45,000.
Maharashtra a ranar Asabar ta ba da rahoton sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 9,251, inda jimillar adadin da aka samu a jihar ya kai 3,66,368 yayin da mutuwar ta karu da 257, ciki har da 116 a yankin Mumbai Metropolitan (MMR), zuwa 13,389, in ji ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya ta jihar.
An sallami adadin marasa lafiya 7,227 a rana, inda adadin waɗanda suka warke ya kai 2,07,194.
Kimanin mutane miliyan 8.85 sun warke zuwa yanzu; yawan masu warkewa ya kai kashi 63.91 a safiyar yau.
Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar - kashi na marasa lafiya da suka gwada tabbatacce ga coronavirus - ya kai kashi 11.
A farkon wannan makon, gwamnati ta ce tana da burin rage yawan masu kamuwa da cutar zuwa kashi 5.
Karnataka a ranar Asabar ta yi rijistar sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus sama da 5,000 a rana ta uku a jere, inda ta wuce 90,000.
Bengaluru kadai ta bayar da rahoton sabbin mutane 2,036 inda jimillar adadin ya kai 43,503.
Babban Minista Arvind Kejriwal ya ce a ranar Asabar, Delhi ta inganta matsayinta a yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 kuma a halin yanzu tana matsayi na takwas tsakanin jihohi da yankuna na tarayya a kasar.
A cikin mafi girman ƙaruwar rana guda, Kerala a ranar Asabar ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutane 1,103 da suka kamu da COVID-19 wanda ya kawo adadin kamuwa da cutar zuwa 18,098, yayin da sama da mutane miliyan 1.5 ke karkashin kulawa.
Mutane 9,420 suna karkashin magani saboda cutar coronavirus.
Rahotanni na gwamnati sun nuna cewa, a cikin awanni 24 da suka gabata, an samu sabbin mutane 6,989 da suka kamu da cutar korona a Tamil Nadu, wanda kuma shi ne mafi girma a cikin kwana daya.
Mutum 89 sun mutu kuma 7,758 sun warke a cikin awanni 24 da suka gabata.
Jimlar masu cutar a jihar yanzu sun kai 2,06,737.
A ranar Asabar, Gujarat ta yi rikodin mafi girma a cikin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus tare da sabbin kamuwa da cutar 1,081, inda jimillar ta kai 54,712 yayin da marasa lafiya 22 suka mutu, ciki har da 11 a Surat, in ji sashen kiwon lafiya na jihar.
Babban Ministan Maharashtra Uddhav Thackeray zai kaddamar da shirin bayar da gudummawar jini a ranar 27 ga Yuli, bayan "Plasma Daan Sankalp Abhiyan" don fara duba marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da suka warke a yankin Dharavi na Mumbai.
Indiya, ƙasa ta uku mafi muni a cikin adadin coronavirus na duniya bayan Amurka da Brazil, a hankali ta haɓaka ƙarfin gwajin COVID-19 kuma ta gudanar da gwaje-gwaje sama da 4.2 a cikin rana, in ji Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta Tarayya a ranar Asabar, tana ba da gudummawar karuwar ga adadin dakunan gwaje-gwaje don nasarar.
Cutar ta kashe mutane sama da 6,33,000 a duniya tun lokacin da ta bullo a China a karshen shekarar da ta gabata, tare da kamuwa da mutane sama da miliyan 15.5, a cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na AFP.
