Shuaib ya yi wannan furuci ne yayin da yake karbar wakilin WHO a Najeriya a ofishinsa a ranar Litinin.
Ya ce Najeriya za ta samu takardar shaidar kawar da cutar Polio a Afirka a watan Agusta daga Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya.
Wannan ya biyo bayan gamsuwa da Hukumar kawar da cutar Polio a kasashen Afirka (ARCC) game da kokarin gwamnati na nuna kawar da cutar Polio a Afirka.
Za a tuna cewa a watan Agusta 2016, cutar shan inna ta bulla a Najeriya bayan shekaru uku da babu wata annobar a kasar.
Barkewar cutar a shekarar 2016 ta hana Najeriya da Afirka samun takardar shaidar kawar da cutar Polio.
Bayan wannan Shuaib ya ce gwamnati ba za ta kasa ganin cewa an kawar da cututtukan da ke shafar yara ƙanana ba, musamman waɗanda za a iya kawar da su ta hanyar rigakafi.
Mulombo ya yaba da kokarin da gwamnati ke yi na inganta bangaren kiwon lafiya, musamman cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya na farko a kasar.
Saudi Arabia: Musulmai kalilan ne kawai za su yi aikin hajji.
A Saudi Arabiya, mahajjata suna shirin fara aikin hajji na wannan shekara, amma annobar Corona tana iyakance adadin mahajjata Musulmai da ke son zuwa.
Mutane 10,000 ne kawai, ciki har da 'yan asalin kasar da kuma kasashen waje da ke zaune a kasar, za su iya yin aikin hajji, bisa ga wasu sabbin dokoki masu tsauri da aka kafa don kiyaye wannan wajibi na addini.
Saudi Arabiya na ɗaya daga cikin ƙasashen Gabas ta Tsakiya da ke da mafi yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar Covid-19, inda mutane 2,733 suka mutu daga cikin sama da 260,000 da suka kamu da cutar.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko a tarihi da aka dauki matakai don hana mahajjata daga wasu sassan duniya shiga aikin hajji.
Ma'aikatar aikin Hajji ta ce wajibi ne saboda tsoron yaduwar cutar Coronavirus.
Labaran Yarima Harry: Abokin Duke na Sussex ya yi ta kai hari kan ikirarin fashewa a sabon littafinsa
Mista Stott ya shaida wa Sky News cewa Yarima Harry da Meghan Markle cewa abun cikin littafin bai bambanta da na jaridun tabloid ba sai dai a cikin takarda mai wuya.
Tsohon sojan ya ce a mai da hankali sosai ga nagarta da ma'auratan suke yi, har da aikin agaji da suke yi.
Mista Stott ya ce: "Ina ganin abin da muke karantawa a nan ba ya bambanta da abin da muka karanta a jaridu masu tasowa, yanzu an buga shi ne kawai a kan takarda mai wuya".
"Kuna da mutum na marubuci, har yanzu ba a tabbatar da cewa ya fito daga gare su ba".
"Ina ganin wani irin hari ne kamar yadda jaridun ke kokarin tsananta musu".
"Na fahimci cewa suna cikin idon jama'a kuma mutane suna son sanin abin da suke yi amma ina fata a fi mai da hankali kan kyawawan abubuwan da suke yi da kuma aikin sadaka maimakon sirrinsu na sirri".
"Amma saboda su wanene ba za su taba tserewa daga wannan ba".
A ranar Asabar wani masanin tarihin masarautar ya kuma bayyana cewa Duke da Duchess na Sussex da ke goyon bayan Sarauniya sun "shafe" sauran mambobin gidan sarauta.
Dr Kate Williams ta shaida wa Sky News cewa dangin sarauta ba su iya amfani da ikon tauraron Yarima Harry da Meghan Markle ba.
Mai sharhi na masarautar ya kara da cewa dangin masarautar suna da tsananin matsayi amma ba za a iya jagorantar ko sarrafa bukatun jama'a ba.
Ta ci gaba: "Ainihin abin da suka yi don tallafa wa Sarauniya sau da yawa yana rufe sauran membobin dangin sarauta kuma an ga wannan a matsayin matsala".
"Suna da wannan iko mai girma na taurari".
"Suna da karamin aure fiye da yawancin 'yan'uwa a matsayi guda, Andrew yana da babban bikin aure, Anne yana da babban bikin aure".
"Suna da karamin bikin aure amma duk da haka ɗaukar auren Harry da Meghan duk da cewa ya fi karami har yanzu yana da girma kamar na William da Kate saboda akwai sha'awar duniya game da su".
Delhi Metro ta kaddamar da tashar jirgin ruwa ta farko a karkashin aikin Phase-4
Jami'ai sun ce a ranar Lahadi, Metro ta Delhi ta kai wani babban mataki a aikin Mataki na 4 yayin da ta fara yin layin farko a kan hanyar da ake ginawa ta Janakpuri West-RK Ashram Marg.
An jefa tashar jirgin ruwa a Keshopur a kan tsayin da ke tsakanin Keshopur da Mukarba Chowk a daren Asabar.
"Kamfanin Jirgin Sama na Delhi ya ɗauki wani muhimmin mataki a gaba a aikin gina Mataki na 4 yayin da aka jefa farkon tashar jirgin a kan hanyar Metro ta Janakpuri West-RK Ashram Marg", in ji DMRC a cikin wata sanarwa.
An cimma wannan "babban ci gaba na gini", duk da tsananin karancin ma'aikata da sauran kalubale na kayan aiki saboda annobar, in ji jami'ai.
Matsakaicin tsayin tashoshin a kan wannan hanyar shine mita 10.
Koyaya, piers za su kasance 20m a Madhuban Chowk (hawan tare da Layi 1) da 25m a Haiderpur Badli Mor inda wannan layin zai haye Layi 2.
A Haiderpur Badli Mor, matakin viaduct zai kasance 28m, mafi girma a tarihin Delhi Metro, in ji sanarwar.
A halin yanzu, mafi girman wuri shine a Dhaula Kuan, inda layin 7 viaduct ya wuce a tsayin 23.6m.
Piers, a cikin yanayin injiniyan injiniya sune gine-ginen ɗaukar kaya waɗanda ke aiki azaman tallafi na tsakiya don ƙarshen ƙarshen spans biyu.
Suna samar da gine-ginen tallafi na tsaye wanda aka ɗaga manyan hanyoyin metro.
Gidajen Metro a yau suna cike da hanyoyi masu yawa a Delhi wanda ta hanyar da aka ɗaga hanyoyin Metro.
Lambobin tashar jiragen ruwa yanzu muhimman alamomi ne ga adiresoshin a duk faɗin Delhi-NCR.
Hanyar ta 28.92 kilomita mai tsawon Janakpuri West-RK Ahsram Marg wani tsawo ne na Layin Magenta kuma zai zo da tashoshi 22.
Yayin da za a ɗaga kilomita 21.18 na wannan hanyar, za a yi kilomita 7.74 a ƙarƙashin ƙasa.
An fara aikin gini a wannan sashin a watan Disamba na shekarar da ta gabata.
A ranar 17 ga Yuli, an fara aikin a sashin karkashin kasa na wannan hanyar tare da fara aikin ginin D Wall a tashar Metro ta Krishna Park Extension.
A ranar 24 ga Yuni, DMRC ta fara aikin simintin U-girders wanda za a girka a ɓangaren da ke kan wannan hanyar.
A karkashin Mataki na 4, za a gina sabbin layin metro mai tsawon kilomita 61.679 a cikin hanyoyi daban-daban guda uku da suka kunshi tashoshin metro 45.
Waɗannan sabbin sassan za su samar da haɗin kai tsakanin sassan da ke aiki a yanzu na Delhi Metro.
Daga cikin wannan, kilomita 22.35 za su kasance a karkashin kasa yayin da sauran za a ɗaga.
Babban Kwamitin Harkokin Musulunci ya kalubalanci Shekau.
A wani taron manema labarai da majalisar ta yi a Kaduna dangane da barazanar da Shekau ta yi a wani bidiyo da ta fitar, lokaci ya yi da Shugaba Muhammadu Buhari zai farka kan wadannan kalubalen.
Daya daga cikin manyan malaman addinin musulunci na Najeriya, Sheikh Abdulwahab Abdullahi Mohammad, ya kalubalanci shugaban Boko Haram Abubakar Shekau kan wani bidiyo da ya fitar inda ya ce idan da gaske shi jarumi ne, to ya kamata ya fito daga ɓoye ya fuskanci jami'an tsaro.
Wannan ya zo ne a lokacin da yanayin tsaro a Najeriya ke kara jan hankalin jama'a, musamman idan aka yi la'akari da barazanar tsaro da kasar ke fuskanta a watan Fabrairu.
Najeriya na samun tallafi na dala miliyan 890 don yaki da cututtuka daga 'Global Fund'.
Kungiyar "Global Fund" ta bayar da dala miliyan 890 ga gwamnatin Najeriya don yaki da cututtuka a kasar.
Waɗannan cututtuka sun haɗa da cutar AIDS, zazzabin cizon sauro da kuma tarin fuka.
Ministan lafiya Osagie Ehanire ya sanar da hakan a makon da ya gabata a Abuja.
Ehanire ya ce tallafin zai taimaka wajen inganta bangaren kiwon lafiya na kasar, musamman wajen yaki da wadannan cututtuka da suka ci gaba a Najeriya.
Za a tuna cewa a watan Janairun 2020 Gwamnatin Tarayya ta sanar da cewa za ta ci bashin dala miliyan 890 daga Asusun Kudi na Duniya don dakile yaduwar cutar a kasar.
Gwamnati ta ce za ta kashe kuɗin ne don yaƙi da cutar kanjamau, zazzabin cizon sauro da cutar tarin fuka daga 2021 zuwa 2023.
Gwamnati ta ce yaƙi da zazzabin cizon sauro zai sami kashi mafi girma na kuɗin, wato dala miliyan 417, na cutar HIV da AIDS, dala miliyan 329, da na tarin fuka dala miliyan 143.
Ya kara da cewa gwamnati ta kafa matakan da za su taimaka mata wajen gudanar da harkokin kudi ta hanyar da ta fi dacewa ba tare da kowa ya fada ta hanyar fashewa ba.
An kashe 'yar fim Spencer Grammer a wajen gidan cin abinci na Manhattan
NEW YORK -- Jaruma Spencer Grammer ta ce tana kokarin kwantar da hankalin wani mutum mai tashin hankali lokacin da ya sare mata hannu ya kuma daka wa abokinta wuka a baya ranar Juma'a a wajen wani gidan cin abinci na birnin New York.
Grammer, mai shekara 36, ta shaida wa US Weekly cewa ita da abokinta "sun yi abin da kowa zai yi a cikin irin wannan yanayi" kuma suna "ƙoƙarin hana rikici daga ƙaruwa" lokacin da aka kai musu hari.
Kakata da abokinta mai shekaru 32 suna cin abinci a teburin waje a The Black Ant a unguwar East Village ta Manhattan da misalin karfe 11:30 na yamma.
A ranar Juma'a lokacin da mutumin ya zo ya bukaci a yi masa hidima yayin da gidan cin abinci ke rufewa.
An ji wa kakarta da abokinta rauni yayin da suka "yi kokarin kawo karshen takaddama tsakanin namiji da ba a san ko wanene ba da sauran masu amfani a wurin", in ji 'yan sanda.
Mutumin ya gudu bayan ya raunata Grammer a hannun dama da abokinta a cikin ƙananan baya tare da wani abu mai kaifi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ba a kama kowa ba.
Grammer, wanda ke ba da muryar Summer a cikin "Rick da Morty" kuma a baya ya yi wasa a cikin ABC Family jerin "Greek, " ita ce 'yar tauraron "Frasier" Kelsey Grammer da kuma actress Doreen Alderman.
Kakata ta ce ita da abokinta suna sa ran su warke da sauri.
Ta ce ba su da wani rauni mai tsanani a ciki.
A cikin sanarwar ta ga Us Weekly, Grammer ta gode wa masu ba da amsa na farko da ma'aikatan asibitin Bellevue da suka kula da su kuma ta lura da "yaƙin da ba za a iya yarda da shi ba" waɗanda ma'aikatan suka yi yaƙi da annobar coronavirus.
"Ya motsa mu sosai mu sami zarafin gode musu da kanmu", in ji Grammer.
INEC Za Ta Fara Rijistar Masu Zabe A 2021
Hukumar Zabe Mai Zaman Kanta ta Kasa (INEC) ta ce za ta fara yin rajistar masu jefa kuri'a a farkon watanni uku na shekara mai zuwa.
Shugaban hukumar, Farfesa Mahmood Yakubu, ya bayyana hakan ne a wani taron manema labarai jim kadan bayan ya bayyana a gaban kwamitin majalisar dattawa kan INEC don kare kasafin kudin hukumar na 2021.
Ya ce za su kwashe lokaci mai tsawo suna gudanar da rajistar masu jefa kuri'a inda za a dakatar da rajistar da watanni shida kafin babban zaben 2023.
"Kwamitinmu na da niyyar ci gaba da wannan aikin na rajistar masu jefa kuri'a a cikin watanni uku na farko na 2021, "in ji shi.
Da zarar mun koma aiki, zai ci gaba da gudana har shekara daya da rabi, a takaice zai kasance kusan watanni shida kafin babban zaben 2023.
Ya ce, idan suka koma aiki, ba za su yi shi kawai a mako ko kowane wata ba, amma a maimakon haka, za a ci gaba da yin aikin, duk da haka, ba za su yi shi cikin hanzari ba amma za su bi shi a hankali suna tattara komai.
Shugaban ya ce INEC a halin yanzu tana fuskantar shari'o'i har 1,700 da suka shafi kafin da bayan zaben 2019.
Ya ce, shari'o'in kotu suna cinye albarkatunsu amma duk da haka suna ƙoƙarin bin matakan da doka ta tanada a matsayin martani ga duk wata karar da aka shigar a kansu.
"Duk wanda ya je kotu ya hada da INEC a cikin shari'ar da aka shigar. Muna da kusan shari'o'i 1,700 daga kafin da bayan zaben 2019. Muna ci gaba da amfani da iyakantattun albarkatunmu", in ji shi.
Yayin da yake kare kasafin kudin hukumar a gaban majalisar dattawa, Yakubu ya shaida wa 'yan majalisar cewa hukumar na shirin janye naira biliyan 5.2 daga naira biliyan 10 da ke cikin baitulmalin INEC don karawa kasafin kudin 2020.
Ya ce biliyan 10 da suke magana a kai wani bangare ne na tanadin hukumar tun lokacin da aka kaddamar da ita a 2010.
Ya ce bukatar yin hakan ya zama dole saboda karancin kasafin kudin 2020 da suka samu daga baya da kuma matsalolin da suka fuskanta, gami da gaskiyar cewa barkewar cutar Corona ta sa hukumar ba ta sami cikakken kasafin kudin 2020 kamar yadda aka tsara ba.
Game da 'yan Najeriya da ke zaune a kasashen waje, ya ce akwai dokar da ta ba su damar kada kuri'a a lokacin zabe, ya kara da cewa da zarar dokar ta fara aiki za su iya samun damar kada kuri'a daga kasashen da suke zaune.
Dan majalisar Val Demings yayi magana game da takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, ya yi wa Trump barazana saboda neman afuwa
'Yar majalisa Val Demings (D-Fla.) ba ta ji kunya game da shirye-shiryenta ta zama mataimakin shugaban kasa a karkashin gwamnatin Joe Biden mai yuwuwa ba tare da nuna godiyarta ta gaske da aka yi la'akari da wannan rawar ba.
A cikin hirar kai tsaye da BlackPressUSA a matsayin wani ɓangare na jerin #FIYAH! kai tsaye, memba mai daraja na Black Caucus na Majalisa ya raba tarihinta da ɗabi'ar aiki da jajircewa wanda ya kawo ta zuwa wannan lokacin, yana mai cewa, "Duk kun san tarihin na. Na girma a matsayin 'yar mai hidima da mai tsaron gida a Jacksonville, Florida. "
Demings ya yi aiki a matsayin daya daga cikin Manajan Ma'aikatan Majalisar Dattijai bakwai a lokacin shari'ar Janairu na Shugaba Donald Trump a Majalisar Dattijai.
Ko da kuwa majalisar dattijai ta wanke shi, tarihi zai rubuta har abada cewa shi ne kwamandan soja na hudu da aka tsige.
Tsohon Manajan Majalisa na Majalisa, ya amsa a cikin wata hira da NPR a watan Fabrairu daga ofishinta na Capitol Hill, "Shin ya cancanci hakan? Kowace rana ya cancanci hakan".
Ya kara da cewa, yayin da hukuncin ya kasance abin takaici, 'yan Democrat suna da wajibi su ci gaba da shari'ar ba tare da la'akari da sakamakon ba.
A yayin hirar, Demings ta bayyana cewa ta yi adawa da Trump ya sauya hukuncin daurin Roger Stone, wanda aka yanke masa hukuncin karya ga Majalisa (a tsakanin sauran laifuka) da kuma yafe wasu masu laifi da aka yanke musu hukuncin aikata laifuka makamancin haka, yana mai cewa, "Halin gafarar abokanka, wadanda suka yi ƙarya da yaudara don rufe laifofinka. "
Demings yana kan jerin sunayen Biden na yiwuwar abokan takara tare da Shugaban CBC Karen Bass (D-Calif.), Tsohuwar Wakilin Jihar Georgia Stacey Abrams, Sanata Kamala Harris (D-Calif.) da Tammy Duckworth (D-Illinois), Magajin garin Atlanta Keisha Lance Bottoms, Tsohuwar Jakadan Amurka Susan Rice da wasu 'yan kaɗan.
Ta lura duk da haka, cewa mutum daya ne kawai zai yanke shawarar wanda zai yi takara tare da Joe Biden a wannan kaka.
"Wannan shi ne Joe Biden".
Sai ta ɗaga hannunta ta miƙa wa lebe ta yi musu wa'azi, ta ce, "Idan kuna son ku yi magana... ku yi hakan".
Babu shakka cewa ko da kuwa halin siyasa na mutum, tarihi zai duba baya a wannan lokacin a matsayin lokacin juyin halitta a siyasar Amurka da kuma fahimta.
Wannan gaskiyar ba ta ɓace ba a kan Demings.
Ta lura cewa samun kowane mata a cikin la'akari don takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa yana wakiltar dama don karya abin da ya rage na rufin gilashi - musamman idan ya zo ga matan Afirka na Amurka.
"Waɗannan su ne ainihin damar da na yi aiki tuƙuru a dukan rayuwata don in samar wa yara maza da mata da wataƙila an gaya musu cewa ba su da launi, ba su da isasshen kuɗi, ko kuma ba su da jinsi", in ji ta.
'Yar majalisar ta yi alkawarin tabbatar da cewa kwamitin dimokradiyya na kasa da kamfen din Biden suna tallatawa da kuma yin aiki tare da jaridar Black Press of America don samun mutane da yawa su yi zabe.
"Zan kira Tom Perez [Shugaban DNC] kuma zan saka wannan a saman jerin na", Demings ya yi alkawari.
Ta amince cewa ya kamata a yi shi yanzu, maimakon daga baya a cikin yakin neman zabe.
Da yake amsawa ga shawarar da tsohon Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Hillary Clinton ya yi cewa Trump zai iya ki barin Fadar White House idan aka kayar da shi, da kuma wani labarin da ya kebanta da cewa shugaban yana kan hanyar ya yafe wa kansa, Demings ya zama mai rai, "Ko da ma ya ba da shawarar ya yafe wa kansa ya sa ni ciwon ciki. "
"Amma wa zai taɓa yin hakan sai dai Trump?
Ina tsammanin ya ƙi aikin.
Ba aikin da za a bar ka ka karya doka ka kuma yi watsi da Tsarin Mulki ba.
Ina tsammanin ya ƙi aikin, amma ya ƙi ya rasa.
Ina ganin wannan shugaban ba ya son barin fadar White House, amma muna da hanyar da za mu kula da hakan, kuma idan hakan ta faru, ina so in kasance cikin tawagar da za ta sa hakan ya faru".
Kotun Duniya ta fara binciken zanga-zangar EndSARS.
Kotun kasa da kasa da ke shari'anta wadanda suka aikata manyan laifuka, wato kotun hukunta laifuka ta kasa da kasa (ICC), ta fara gudanar da binciken ta na farko dangane da tashe-tashen hankula da suka barke a yayin zanga-zangar neman kawo karshen bangaren 'yan sanda, #EndSARS, da ta gudana a fadin Najeriya.
Ofishin mai gabatar da kara na Kotun ta Duniya ta Duniya ya shaida a cikin wata sanarwa da ya fitar yana mai cewa ya sami bayanai game da laifukan da ake zargin an aikata su yayin zanga-zangar da suka juya zuwa tashin hankali da lalata dukiya da dukiyar gwamnati da na jama'a.
Masu zanga-zanga sun kwashe makonni da dama a kan titunan biranen kasar suna zanga-zanga don adawa da cin zarafin da jami'an 'yan sanda ke yi.
Kimanin fararen hula 51, 'yan sanda 11 da sojoji bakwai ne suka mutu, a cewar shugaban Najeriya Muhammadu Buhari lokacin da ya ba da shawarar ga al'ummar duniya yadda za a shawo kan matsalar.
Kungiyar kare hakkin dan adam, Amnesty International, ta ce jami'an tsaro sun bude wuta kan masu zanga-zanga, inda suka kashe da kuma raunata mutane da dama.
Sojoji da 'yan sanda duk sun musanta zargin Amnesty International, amma kotun ta ICC ta ce za ta fitar da sakamakon binciken ta na farko ga jama'a.
Zanga-zangar EndSARS, wacce ta fara a Legas da Abuja, ta kuma bazu zuwa wasu jihohin kasar, kafin ta zama tashin hankali, wanda ya haifar da asarar rayuka da dukiya a cikin al'ummominsu.
Wasu da ake zargin masu fashin baki ne suka yi amfani da zanga-zangar wajen lalata gine-ginen gwamnati da na wasu 'yan siyasa, musamman a jihar Legas, a yankin kudu maso yammacin kasar.
Hukumomi sun tura 'yan sanda masu hana tarzoma don dakile lamarin, amma tashin hankali ya ci gaba da ƙaruwa sakamakon kashe masu zanga-zanga a Lekki.
Masu zanga-zanga sun zargi jami'an tsaro da bude musu wuta a Lekki, jihar Legas, wanda shine cibiyar da ake gudanar da zanga-zangar, zanga-zangar da ta bar mutane da yawa sun ji rauni.
Wasu na ganin cewa harbin da aka yi wa masu zanga-zanga ya sa lamarin ya kara tabarbarewa, musamman a jihar Legas.
