Coleen Rooney ta dauki lauyan Johnny Depp don yakin Wagatha Christie da Rebekah Vardy
Mrs Rooney ta nemi David Sherborne ya yi yaƙi da zargin da ta yi na bata sunan Mrs Vardy
Bayan tattaunawar tsakanin WAGs ta gaza, masu ciki suna tsammanin wasan kwaikwayo mai ban mamaki
Coleen Rooney ta dauki hayar wani sanannen lauya da ke wakiltar Johnny Depp a cikin shari'ar cin hanci da rashawa da ya yi domin wakiltar ta a cikin shari'ar "Wagatha Christie" da Rebekah Vardy.
Jaridar Mail on Sunday ta fahimci cewa Mrs Rooney ta umarci David Sherborne da ya yi yaki da zargin da ta yi wa Mrs Vardy da zargin cewa an leaked bayanan sirri daga asusun Instagram na sirri zuwa jarida.
Labarin ya zo ne kwanaki bayan da takardun da aka gabatar a Kotun Koli suka yi ikirarin cewa Mrs Vardy, wacce ta auri dan wasan gaba na Leicester City Jamie Vardy, ta sha wahala ta jiki da ta tunani sakamakon zargin da Mrs Rooney ta yi.
Jaridun sun ce mahaifiyar 'ya'ya biyar mai shekara 38 "ta sha wahala daga mummunan tashin hankali da damuwa wanda ya bayyana a cikin jin tsoron barin gida", suna ƙara cewa Mrs Vardy, wacce take da ciki na watanni bakwai a lokacin, "an kai ta asibiti sau uku... yayin da ta sha wahala daga tashin hankali sakamakon post ɗin da kuma sakamakonsa. "
Bayan wakiltar Depp a shari'ar sa da ya yi wa jaridar The Sun kan zargin da ake masa na cewa shi dan wasan ya yi wa matarsa bulala, Mr Sherborne, mai shekaru 50, yana wakiltar Duke da Duchess na Sussex a cikin kararsu ta sirri da suka yi wa Associated Newspapers, masu wallafa jaridar The Mail a ranar Lahadi.
Bayan tattaunawar sasantawa tsakanin WAGs biyu ta gaza, masu ciki yanzu suna tsammanin wasan kwaikwayo a kotun.
"Idan kun yi tunanin shari'ar Depp ta kasance akwatin gidan, kada ku raina wannan yakin WAG mai zuwa", in ji wata majiya.
"Game da gaske ne yanzu. Coleen ba za ta ja da baya ba, haka ma Becky. Za ta zama abin mamaki".
Mrs Rooney ta yi ikirarin cewa wani ya yi amfani da asusun Mrs Vardy na Instagram ya zubo labaran karya game da ita zuwa jarida.
An ba ta sunan "Wagatha Christie" bayan ta bayyana yadda ta shafe watanni biyar tana rage yawan abokai da za su iya ganin sabuntawarta a kan labarun Instagram har sai da asusun Mrs Vardy ya rage.
