Tsohon Gwamnan Jihar Borno kuma Sanata mai wakiltar Borno ta Tsakiya a Majalisar Dattawan Najeriya, Alhaji Kashim Shettima, ya bayyana dalla-dalla kalubalen da ya fuskanta kafin ya iya gano zababben Gwamnan Jihar Borno, Farfesa Babagana Umara Zulum, a matsayin magajinsa a kujerar gwamnan jihar da zai bar kamar yadda za a gudanar da zaben 2019. Ya ce yana neman dan siyasa wanda yake da gaskiya da abin dogaro.
