Halin rashin hankali na Amurka yana haifar da babbar barazana ga zaman lafiya da tsaro na duniya.
A jerin tarurruka na babban matakin da aka yi domin bikin cika shekaru 75 da kafa Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya a watan Satumba, Ministan Harkokin Wajen Cuba Bruno Rodrigurz ya bayyana wannan.
