Corona: Mutane 137 sun kamu da cutar Corona a Najeriya a ranar Talata.
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Kasa (NCDC) ta sanar da karin mutane 137 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus a Najeriya a ranar Talata.
Alkaluman da hukumar NCDC ta fitar a ranar Talata sun nuna cewa jihar Legas tana da karin mutane 60, Abia-21, FCT-18, Rivers-13, Kaduna-5, Oyo-4, Edo-3, Delta-2, Imo-2, Ogun-2, Bauchi-1, Gombe-1, Nasarawa-1 Niger-1 da Osun-1.
Ya zuwa yanzu mutane 63,173 ne suka kamu da cutar a Najeriya, 59,634 sun warke, kuma 1,151 sun mutu.
Bayan haka, wasu mutane 2,375 sun kamu da cutar a Najeriya.
Jihar Legas har yanzu tana da mafi yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar, da 21,398 masu kamuwa da cutar, FCT -6,142, Oyo -3,456, Edo -2,669, Delta -1,816, Rivers 2,844, Kano -1,749, Ogun -2,053, Kaduna -2,663, Katsina -953, Ondo -1,669, Borno -745, Gombe -938, Bauchi -713, Ebonyi -1,049, Plateau -3,652, Enugu -1,314, Abia -898, Imo -619, Jigawa -325, Kwara -1,069, Bayelsa -413, Nasarawa -483, Osun -930, Sokoto -165, Niger -277, Akwa Ibom -295, Benue -493, Adamawa -252, Anambra -277, Kebbi -93, Zamfara -79, 79, Yobe -335, Ekiti -335.
Yana yiwuwa mutumin da ya kamu da cutar Corona zai samu matsalolin lafiyar kwakwalwa.
Likitoci a Jami'ar UCL a Burtaniya sun bayyana cewa yana yiwuwa mutumin da ya kamu da cutar Corona zai iya samun matsalolin rashin lafiyar kwakwalwa.
Jagoran wannan bincike kuma jami'in UCL Ross Paterson ya sanar da cewa ya zama dole a yi karin bincike don sanin irin raunin da cutar ke iya haifarwa a cikin mutum.
Cutar kwayar cutar Corona tana ɗaya daga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta da ke sa mutum ya kamu da sanyi na yau da kullun, wanda idan ya yi tsanani, zai iya haifar da wahalar numfashi, wanda ake kira Ciwon Numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV), da kuma cututtukan da ke iya toshe makogwaro.
Amma Corona Virus sabuwar cuta ce wacce ba a taɓa gano ta a jikin mutum ba.
Alamun kamuwa da cuta sun hada da matsaloli tare da hanyoyin numfashi a cikin makogwaro watau rashin numfashi, zazzabi mai yawa, tsananin tari, da ciwon makogwaro.
Idan kuma ciwon ya yi tsanani, zai iya sa mutum ya kasa numfashi, sai kuma ya kamu da ciwon huhu, kuma idan ya yi tsanani sosai, koda na mutumin zai daina aiki gaba ɗaya.
Akwai wasu matakan gaggawa da ke taimakawa wajen kaucewa wannan kamuwa, kamar wanke hannu sau da yawa da sabulu da ruwa, da kuma rufe hanci da baki koyaushe lokacin da kake tari.
Kafin cin nama da ƙwai, ka riƙa tsabtace su kuma ka dafa su sosai.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bukaci mutane su nisanta kansu daga duk wanda ke nuna alamun rashin lafiya, musamman waɗanda aka ambata a sama, kuma su je asibiti nan da nan don a yi musu magani idan ba su da lafiya.
