An Kama Uba Da Ɗansa Tare Da Heroin Na Kimanin Rupees 1.54 A Mizoram
An yi safarar heroin, mai darajar kusan Rs 1.55 crore a kasuwar gida, daga Myanmar: 'Yan sanda
An kama wani mutum da dansa da heroin kilo 1.9 a gundumar Hnahthial ta Mizoram kusa da iyakar Myanmar, in ji 'yan sanda a ranar Lahadi.
An yi safarar heroin, mai darajar kusan Rs 1.55 crore a kasuwar gida, daga Myanmar, in ji su.
An kama Duhkima (62) da dansa Remthangpuia (33) tare da miyagun kwayoyi a daren Juma'a daga kauyen Ngharchhip, in ji 'yan sanda.
Sun kuma jefa kimanin gram 280 na heroin, mai darajar Rs 15 lakh, yayin da suke iyo a kan kogi yayin da suke kokarin tserewa daga 'yan sanda, in ji jami'ai.
A cewar 'yan sanda, an yi imanin cewa an kama mafi yawan heroin a jihar.
An tuhumi wadanda ake tuhuma a karkashin sassan da suka dace na Dokar Magungunan Narcotic da Magungunan Psychotropic (NDPS), 1985.
Ko da yake iyakokin tsakanin jihohi da wanda ke tare da Myanmar sun kasance a rufe bayan barkewar cutar coronavirus, safarar miyagun ƙwayoyi da sauran kayayyakin da aka yi ta fataucin mutane sun ci gaba ba tare da raguwa ba, in ji majiyoyin 'yan sanda.
Assam Rifles sun kama manyan motoci 25 da ke dauke da kwayoyin betel, masu darajar Rs 4 crore, da ake safarar su daga Myanmar, in ji su.
Mick Fleetwood ya ba da girmamawa ga Peter Green: 'Waƙar sa za ta rayu'
Mick Fleetwood ya miƙa gudummawa ga Peter Green, wanda ya kafa Fleetwood Mac, wanda ya mutu a yau yana da shekaru 73.
Green memba ne na asalin rukunin dutsen, tare da Mick da aka ambata, da kuma Jeremy Spencer.
Duk da barin ƙungiyar a cikin 1970 kafin manyan nasarorin su tare da kundi kamar Rumours, Mick ya ba da girmamawa ga tsohon abokin aikinsa, yana tabbatar wa magoya baya cewa "waƙarsa za ta rayu".
Fleetwood ya gaya wa PA: "A gare ni, da kowane memba na baya da na yanzu na Fleetwood Mac, rasa Peter Green abu ne mai ban mamaki.
"Peter ne ya kafa ƙungiyar Fleetwood Mac tare da ni, John McVie, da Jeremy Spencer.
Babu wanda ya taɓa shiga cikin sahun Fleetwood Mac ba tare da girmamawa ga Peter Green da baiwarsa ba, da kuma gaskiyar cewa ya kamata kiɗa ya haskaka da haske kuma koyaushe a kawo shi tare da sha'awar rashin sassauci. "
Tsohon mawaƙin mai shekaru 73 ya daɗa: "Peter, zan yi kewarka, amma ka huta, ka ji daɗin kiɗan da kake yi.
Na gode da kuka tambaye ni in zama mai buga muku drum duk shekarun da suka gabata.
Mun yi kyau, kuma mun kafa hanya mai kyau ta waƙa don mutane da yawa su more.
"Allah ya yi maka albarka, masoyi na.... kauna Mick Fleetwood".
Da yake tabbatar da mutuwar Green, wata sanarwa daga lauyoyin Swan Turton ta karanta: "Da baƙin ciki mai yawa ne dangin Peter Green suka sanar da mutuwarsa a karshen mako, cikin kwanciyar hankali a cikin barcinsa.
"Za a ba da ƙarin bayani a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa".
Green ya bar 'yarsa, Rosebud Samuels-Greenbaum, wanda ta raba tare da tsohuwar matarsa Jane Samuels.
Green ya kafa Fleetwood Mac tare da abokan aikinsa Mick Fleetwood da Jeremy Spencer, tare da ƙungiyar da aka kira Peter Green's Fleetwood Mac tare da Jeremy Spencer.
Koyaya, mawaƙin mawaƙa zai bar ƙungiyar a cikin 1970, bayan kundi huɗu.
Fleetwood Mac zai ci gaba da samun babban yabo da shahara a duk duniya tare da ƙarin saiti ciki har da Lindsey Buckingham da Stevie Nicks akan sabbin kundin ciki har da jita-jita da Tusk.
Magu ya kalubalanci rahoton kwamitin Ayo Salami.
Lauyan shugaban EFCC da aka dakatar, Ibrahim Magu, ya kalubalanci rahoton da Hukumar Ayo Salami ta fitar inda ta ba da shawarar cewa shugaban ya cire shi domin a gurfanar da shi kan zargin da ake masa.
Wahab Shitu, lauyan Ibrahim Magu ya ce har yanzu bai gama tattara bayanan da za a gabatar ba, duk da jin korafe-korafen da kwamitin Salami ya gabatar.
Ya kara da cewa, a sakamakon zargin da aka yi wa shugaban hukumar yaki da cin hanci da rashawa da aka dakatar, kwamitin bai fitar da kwafin tuhumar da aka yi masa ba.
Shittu ya kuma kara da cewa a matsayinsa na lauyan Ibrahim Magu, har yanzu bai samu damar ganin tuhume-tuhume da sauran zarge-zargen da ake yi wa Magu ba.
